E%5Cn%E2%80%94%20Smt.%20Sudha%20Murty%20(%40SmtSudhaMurty)%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Ftwitter.com%2FSmtSudhaMurty%2Fstatus%2F1825374632331141397%3Fref_src%3Dtwsrc%255Etfw%5C%22%3EAugust%2019%2C%202024%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fblockquote%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20wife%20of%20the%20Infosys%20Chairman%20shared%20the%20story%20behind%20the%20festival%20and%20said%2C%20%26quot%3BIt%20goes%20back%20to%20when%20Rani%20Karnavati%20(from%20the%20Kingdom%20of%20Mewar)%20was%20in%20danger%20her%20kingdom%20was%20small%20and%20under%20attack.%20She%20did%20not%20know%20what%20to%20do.%20She%20sent%20a%20small%20piece%20of%20thread%20to%20Mughal%20Emperor%20Humayun%20and%20said%20I'm%20in%20danger%20please%20consider%20me%20as%20your%20sister.%20Please%20do%20come%20and%20protect%20me.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMs%20Murty%20said%2C%20%26quot%3BHumayun%20did%20not%20know%20what%20it%20was...he%20asked%20what%20is%20this%20and%20the%20locals%20said%20this%20is%20a%20call%20of%20a%20sister%20to%20a%20brother...this%20is%20the%20custom%20of%20the%20land%2C%26quot%3B%20adding%2C%20%26quot%3BThe%20emperor%20said%20okay%20if%20this%20is%20the%20case%20then%20I%20will%20help%20Rani%20Karnavati.%20He%20left%20Delhi%20but%20couldn't%20reach%20there%20on%20time%20and%20Karnavati%20died.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThis%20idea%20is%20when%20you're%20facing%20a%20threat%20or%20in%20distress.%20A%20thread%20indicates%20that%20somebody%20should%20come%20and%20help%20me%20and%20it%20means%20a%20lot...%26quot%3B%20she%20added.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHowever%2C%20several%20users%20on%20X%20differed%20and%20said%20the%20story%20goes%20back%20to%20the%20time%20of%20Mahabharat%20and%20not%20post-medieval%20India.%20Users%20said%2C%20that%20during%20the%20time%20of%20Mahabharat%2C%20Lord%20Krishna%20inadvertently%20cut%20his%20finger%20while%20using%20the%20Sudarshan%20chakra%20to%20kill%20King%20Shishupal.%20Draupadi%20covered%20the%20wound%20with%20a%20piece%20of%20cloth.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3