er-at-night-in-agra-6370640%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Opinion%3A%20The%20Economic%20Rationale%20For%20Amending%20The%20Waqf%20Act%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%3E%3Cimg%20alt%3D%5C%22Latest%20and%20Breaking%20News%20on%20NDTV%5C%22%20title%3D%5C%22Latest%20and%20Breaking%20News%20on%20NDTV%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2024-08%2Friuaib7_waqf_625x300_19_August_24.jpg%5C%22%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EImagine%20waking%20up%20to%20discover%20that%20your%20family's%20ancestral%20land%20-%20where%20your%20roots%20run%20deep%20-%20has%20suddenly%20been%20claimed%20by%20someone%20else.%20This%20isn't%20a%20plot%20twist%20from%20a%20novel%20but%20a%20real-life%20predicament%20faced%20by%20villagers%20in%20Tamil%20Nadu's%20Thiruchendurai.%20Rajagopal%2C%20a%20farmer%20simply%20looking%20to%20sell%20a%20small%20piece%20of%20land%2C%20was%20told%20that%20his%20property%20now%20belonged%20to%20the%20Waqf%20Board.%20The%20sheer%20absurdity%20of%20the%20situation%20is%20reminiscent%20of%20a%20Kafka%20novel%2C%20where%20a%20certain%20machinery%20churns%20out%20decisions%20detached%20from%20reality.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EC.S.%20Lewis%20once%20wrote%2C%20%26quot%3BWhen%20you%20argue%20against%20Him%20you%20are%20arguing%20against%20the%20very%20power%20that%20makes%20you%20able%20to%20argue%20at%20all%26quot%3B.%20The%20landowners%20found%20themselves%20in%20a%20similarly%20paradoxical%20situation%2C%20unable%20to%20contest%20the%20very%20system%20that%20reclassified%20their%20land%20overnight.%20This%20farcical%20scenario%20shows%20the%20urgent%20need%20to%20amend%20the%20Waqf%20Act%2C%20which%2C%20as%20it%20stands%2C%20can%20transform%20long-held%20private%20land%20into%20Waqf%20property%20with%20the%20stroke%20of%20a%20pen%2C%20leaving%20rightful%20owners%20in%20the%20lurch.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch2%3E%3Cstrong%3EWhat%20Exactly%20Is%20A%20Waqf%20Property%3F%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh2%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EA%20Waqf%2C%20under%20the%20Waqf%20Act%20of%201954%2C%20is%20a%20property%20irrevocably%20dedicated%20in%20the%20name%20of%20God%20for%20religious%20and%20charitable%20purposes%2C%20essentially%20rendering%20it%20non-transferable%20and%20perpetually%20detained%20as%20a%20charitable%20act%20towards%20God.%20Governed%20by%20the%20Waqf%20Act%20of%201995%2C%20Waqf%20properties-whether%20public%20or%20private-are%20managed%20by%20a%20'%3Cem%3Emutawali'%C2%A0%3C%2Fem%3Eand%20overseen%20by%20state%20Waqf%20Boards%2C%20which%20wield%20significant%20power%2C%20including%20the%20ability%20to%20sanction%20transfers%20of%20immovable%20properties.%20Outlandishly%2C%20these%20properties%2C%20once%20designated%20as%20Waqf%2C%20are%20locked%20into%20perpetuity%2C%20immune%20to%20dissolution%2C%20and%20detached%20from%20broader%20legal%20frameworks%2C%20such%20as%20the%20Indian%20Trusts%20Act.%20The%20Waqf%20Board%2C%20a%20legal%20entity%20with%20sweeping%20authority%2C%20administers%20these%20properties%2C%20ensuring%20they%20serve%20the%20pious%20purposes%20they%20were%20intended%20for%2C%20and%20the%20Central%20Waqf%20Council%20advises%20and%20monitors%20these%20state-level%20boards.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EOne%20of%20the%20major%20issues%20has%20been%20the%20broad%20powers%20granted%20to%20Waqf%20Boards%2C%20which%20have%20sometimes%20led%20to%20the%20controversial%20declaration%20of%20government%20and%20private%20properties%20as%20Waqf.%20For%20example%2C%20in%20Surat%2C%20the%20entire%20municipal%20corporation%20headquarters%20was%20declared%20as%20Waqf%20property%2C%20raising%20concerns%20about%20the%20overreach%20of%20the%20Waqf%20Board's%20powers.%20Similar%20disputes%20have%20arisen%20in%20other%20parts%20of%20India%2C%20where%20properties%20with%20long%20histories%20have%20suddenly%20been%20declared%20Waqf%2C%20often%20leading%20to%20legal%20battles%20and%20public%20outcry.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch2%3E%3Cstrong%3ELack%20Of%20Data%20And%20Documentation%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh2%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20lack%20of%20clear%20documentation%20and%20the%20potential%20for%20misuse%20of%20the%20Waqf%20Act%20have%20exacerbated%20these%20disputes.%20Courts%20have%20intervened%20in%20some%20cases%2C%20ruling%20that%20the%20Waqf%20Board%20must%20provide%20valid%20documentary%20evidence%20to%20support%20its%20claims.%20Despite%20these%20rulings%2C%20the%20expansive%20powers%20of%20the%20Waqf%20Boards%20continue%20to%20be%20a%20source%20of%20controversy.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EWaqf%20properties%20represent%20the%20third-largest%20landholding%20in%20India%2C%20only%20behind%20the%20Defence%20Ministry%20and%20Indian%20Railways.%20The%20Ministry%20of%20Minority%20Affairs%20has%20a%20portal%20that%20has%20digitised%20the%20data%20for%20these%20vast%20assets%20through%20the%20Waqf%20Assets%20Management%20System%20of%20India%20(WAMSI)%2C%20part%20of%20the%20Qaumi%20Waqf%20Board%20Taraqqiati%20Scheme%20(QWBTS).%20This%20scheme%20aims%20to%20safeguard%20and%20prevent%20encroachment%20of%20Waqf%20properties%20through%20digitisation%20and%20GIS%20mapping.%20However%2C%20despite%20the%20entry%20of%208%2C72%2C324%20immovable%20Waqf%20properties%20into%20WAMSI%20and%20the%20GIS%20mapping%20of%203%2C29%2C995%20properties%2C%20a%20lot%20still%20needs%20to%20be%20done.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAccording%20to%20the%20Waqf%20Management%20System%20of%20India%20(WAMSI)%2C%20the%20status%20of%20Waqf%20properties%20shows%20significant%20management%20and%20documentation%20challenges.%20The%20largest%20category%20of%20properties%2C%20representing%20436%2C169%20units%2C%20has%20no%20information%20available%2C%20indicating%20a%20significant%20gap%20in%20data%20collection%20and%20transparency.%20Additionally%2C%2058%2C898%20properties%20are%20encroached%20upon%2C%20reflecting%20the%20extent%20of%20unauthorised%20occupation.%20There%20are%20also%207%2C831%20properties%20under%20external%20litigation%20and%205%2C371%20under%20internal%20litigation%2C%20highlighting%20the%20legal%20challenges%20faced%20in%20securing%20these%20assets.%20A%20substantial%20portion%20of%20properties%2C%20totalling%203%2C39%2C505%2C%20are%20non-encumbered.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch2%3E%3Cstrong%3EHow%20The%20System%20Has%20Led%20To%20Disputes%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh2%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20process%20of%20declaring%20a%20property%20as%20Waqf%2C%20particularly%20under%20the%20concept%20of%20%26quot%3BWaqf%20by%20use%26quot%3B%2C%20has%20led%20to%20numerous%20legal%20disputes.%20This%20ambiguity%20allows%20for%20conflicting%20claims%20between%20Waqf%20Boards%20and%20other%20stakeholders%2C%20including%20government%20agencies%2C%20leading%20to%20prolonged%20litigation%20and%20delays%20in%20the%20utilisation%20of%20these%20properties%20for%20charitable%20purposes.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EFurther%2C%20the%20Waqf%20Act%20originally%20established%20tribunals%20to%20resolve%20disputes%20over%20Waqf%20properties.%20However%2C%20these%20tribunals%20are%20criticised%20for%20being%20inefficient%20and%20lacking%20judicial%20independence.%20Recent%20amendments%20have%20attempted%20to%20address%20this%20by%20modifying%20their%20composition%2C%20but%20concerns%20remain%20about%20their%20ability%20to%20handle%20complex%20property%20disputes%20effectively.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch2%3E%3Cstrong%3EWhat%20The%20Sachar%20Committee%20Said%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh2%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ESeveral%20committees%20have%20raised%20issues%20with%20the%20Waqf%20Act.%20For%20instance%2C%20while%20introducing%20the%20Waqf%20Amendment%20Bill%202024%20in%20Lok%20Sabha%2C%20the%20Minority%20Affairs%20Minister%20highlighted%20the%201976%20Waqf%20inquiry%20report%2C%20which%20observed%20that%20Waqf%20properties%20were%20controlled%20by%20%3Cem%3EMutawallis%20%3C%2Fem%3Eand%20called%20for%20corrective%20action.%20The%20report%20also%20recommended%20establishing%20a%20tribunal%20to%20resolve%20disputes%20and%20emphasised%20the%20need%20to%20fix%20improper%20audits%20and%20accounts%20of%20Waqf%20boards.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20Sachar%20Committee%20flagged%20the%20issue%20of%20meagre%20revenue%20generation%20from%20Waqf%20properties.%20The%20report%20observed%20that%20annual%20income%20from%20Waqf%20properties%20(in%202005)%20across%20India%20was%20approximately%20%E2%82%B9163%20crore%2C%20representing%20a%20meagre%20rate%20of%20return%20of%20just%202.7%25.%20The%20report%20suggests%20that%20if%20these%20properties%20were%20developed%20and%20put%20to%20efficient%20commercial%20use%2C%20they%20could%20generate%20at%20least%20a%20minimum%20return%20of%2010%25%2C%20translating%20to%20approximately%20%E2%82%B912%2C000%20crores%20per%20annum.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch2%3E%3Cstrong%3EA%20Slew%20Of%20Regulatory%20Issues%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh2%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHistorically%2C%20Waqf%20properties%20have%20faced%20significant%20challenges%2C%20including%20underutilisation%2C%20illegal%20encroachments%2C%20and%20widespread%20mismanagement%2C%20which%20have%20hindered%20their%20ability%20to%20generate%20much-needed%20revenue%20for%20the%20community.%20A%20lack%20of%20strategic%20planning%2C%20evident%20in%20the%20absence%20of%20comprehensive%20business%20plans%2C%20market%20analysis%2C%20and%20risk%20management%20strategies%2C%20has%20contributed%20to%20this%20issue.%20With%20insufficient%20monitoring%20and%20enforcement%2C%20regulatory%20oversight%20has%20been%20weak%2C%20allowing%20properties%20to%20be%20leased%20at%20below-market%20rates%20due%20to%20corruption.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EFinancial%20mismanagement%20has%20further%20compounded%20these%20problems%2C%20with%20funds%20often%20misappropriated%20or%20not%20reinvested%20effectively.%20Additionally%2C%20the%20lack%20of%20community%20involvement%20and%20oversight%20has%20led%20to%20decisions%20being%20made%20without%20adequate%20consultation%2C%20further%20alienating%20the%20intended%20beneficiaries.%20To%20overcome%20these%20challenges%2C%20it%20is%20essential%20to%20implement%20strict%20regulatory%20frameworks%2C%20enforce%20strategic%20business%20plans%2C%20and%20foster%20active%20community%20engagement%2C%20ensuring%20that%20Waqf%20properties%20are%20managed%20effectively%20and%20generate%20sustainable%20revenue%20for%20the%20community.%3Cbr%3E%5Cn%C2%A0%3Cbr%3E%5CnHence%2C%20reforms%20are%20needed.%20Despite%20attempts%20to%20bring%20order%20to%20the%20chaos%2C%20like%20digitising%20records%2C%20the%20system%20still%20feels%20like%20a%20Wild%20West%20of%20land%20claims.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cem%3E(Bibek%20Debroy%20is%20Chairman%2C%20Economic%20Advisory%20Council%20to%20the%20Prime%20Minister%2C%20and%20Aditya%20Sinha%20is%20OSD%2C%20Research%2C%20Economic%20Advisory%20Council%20to%20the%20Prime%20Minister)%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EDisclaimer%3A%20These%20are%20the%20personal%20opinions%20of%20the%20author%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1724064900000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2024-08%2F0ebc575o_waqf_625x300_19_August_24.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Fopinion%2Fthe-economic-rationale-for-amending-the-waqf-act-6370628%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22The%20Sachar%20Committee%20flagged%20the%20meagre%20revenue%20generation%20from%20Waqf%20properties.%20The%20report%20observed%20that%20annual%20income%20from%20Waqf%20properties%20(in%202005)%20across%20India%20was%20approximately%20%E2%82%B9163%20crore%2C%20representing%20a%20meagre%20rate%20of%20return%20of%20just%202.7%25.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Fopinion%2Fthe-economic-rationale-for-amending-the-waqf-act-6370628%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Massive%20Protests%20In%20Kolkata%2C%20Doctors%20Form%20Human%20Chain%2C%20Tie%20Rakhis%20To%20Cops%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cp%3EDoctors%20in%20Kolkata%20took%20to%20the%20streets%20in%20large%20numbers%20today%2C%20forming%20a%20human%20chain%20to%20protest%20the%20rape%20and%20murder%20of%20a%2031-year-old%20postgraduate%20trainee%20doctor%20at%20the%20state-run%20RG%20Kar%20Medical%20College%20and%20Hospital%20on%20August%209.%20A%20massive%20number%20of%20healthcare%20professionals%20formed%20human%20chains%20and%20blocked%20several%20roads%20in%20the%20West%20Bengal%20capital.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAmid%20the%20protests%2C%20a%20unique%20gesture%20stood%20out.%20Protesting%20doctors%20and%20police%20officers%2C%20who%20were%20maintaining%20order%2C%20shared%20a%20moment%20of%20camaraderie.%20Doctors%20tied%20%3Cem%3Erakhis%3C%2Fem%3E%20on%20the%20wrists%20of%20police%20personnel%20and%20in%20return%2C%20the%20cops%20distributed%20toffees%20to%20the%20doctors.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ESeveral%20former%20students%20of%20RG%20Kar%20Medical%20College%2C%20many%20of%20them%20now%20veteran%20doctors%2C%20joined%20the%20protest%20alongside%20their%20younger%20colleagues.%20Some%20of%20whom%20protesting%20had%20graduated%20as%20far%20back%20as%20the%201960s%2C%20holding%20placards%20and%20demanding%20swift%20justice.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BI%20belong%20to%20the%201964%20batch.%20What%20has%20happened%20in%20the%20hospital%20is%20just%20unthinkable%2C%20and%20it%20is%20the%20call%20of%20the%20hour%20to%20hit%20the%20streets%20to%20protest%2C%26quot%3B%20one%20veteran%20doctor%20said%2C%20as%20quoted%20by%20news%20agency%20ANI.%20%26quot%3BWe%20need%20justice.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20ongoing%20protests%20have%20impacted%20healthcare%20services%20across%20West%20Bengal%2C%20particularly%20in%20state-run%20hospitals.%20Junior%20doctors%2C%20who%20have%20been%20at%20the%20forefront%20of%20the%20agitation%2C%20have%20continued%20their%20cease-work%20protest%2C%20demanding%20the%20swift%20punishment%20of%20those%20responsible%20for%20the%20crime%20and%20the%20public%20release%20of%20the%20victim's%20post-mortem%20examination%20report.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EState-run%20hospitals%20witnessed%20long%20queues%20at%20out-patient%20departments%20today%2C