%20inside%20genitalia%2C%20the%20report%20said.%20It%20also%20noted%20haemorrhage%20in%20the%20lungs%20and%20blood%20clots%20in%20other%20parts%20of%20the%20body.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20doctor%20was%20found%20dead%20at%20the%20RG%20Kar%20Medical%20College%20and%20Hospital%20on%20August%209%2C%20sparking%20nationwide%20protests%20and%20strikes%20by%20doctors.%20A%20civic%20volunteer%20named%20Sanjay%20Roy%20was%20arrested%20by%20the%20Kolkata%20Police%20a%20day%20later.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThree%20days%20later%2C%20the%20CBI%20took%20over%20the%20investigation%20on%20the%20direction%20of%20the%20Calcutta%20High%20Court.%20The%20central%20agency%20has%20been%20interrogating%20the%20medical%20college's%20former%20principal%20Sandip%20Ghosh%20for%20four%20days.%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1724061720000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2024-08%2Fc89mkuoo_doctors-protests_625x300_19_August_24.jpeg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fwhat-autopsy-report-of-kolkata-doctor-says-about-injuries-she-suffered-6369414%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22The%20autopsy%20report%20of%20the%20trainee%20doctor%2C%20who%20was%20raped%20and%20murdered%20while%20on%20duty%20at%20a%20Kolkata%20hospital%20last%20week%2C%20details%20injuries%20inflicted%20on%20her%20before%20her%20death.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fwhat-autopsy-report-of-kolkata-doctor-says-about-injuries-she-suffered-6369414%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22What%20is%20lateral%20entry%20into%20bureaucracy%3F%20All%20you%20need%20to%20know%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%22%2C%22published%22%3A1724061628000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.toiimg.com%2Fphoto%2Fmsid-112626896%2Cimgsize-813530.cms%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Ftimesofindia.indiatimes.com%2Findia%2Fwhat-is-lateral-entry-into-bureaucracy-all-you-need-to-know%2Farticleshow%2F