of%20Kolkata's%20RG%20Kar%20Medical%20College%20and%20Hospital%20has%20been%20undergoing%20a%20gruelling%20questioning%20session%20in%20the%20probe%20into%20the%20rape%20and%20murder%20of%20a%20doctor.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fwhat-did-cbi-ask-kolkata-hospital-ex-head-about-doctors-rape-murder-6370141%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22The%20new%20homebuying%20rule%20that%20could%20save%20you%20thousands%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%222000%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Real%20estate%20agent%20and%20future%20home%20buyers%20gazing%20up%20at%20stack%20of%20documents%20with%20a%20house%20perched%20at%20the%20top%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F66bf662d5da406397bf68acd%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%221000%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3E%3Cp%3EGetty%20Images%3B%20Alyssa%20Powell%2FBI%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3EBuying%20a%20new%20home%20has%20always%20been%20stressful%2C%20but%20somewhere%20before%20the%20messy%20stuff%20%E2%80%94%20the%20loan%20applications%2C%20inspections%2C%20contracts%2C%20and%20wire%20transfers%20%E2%80%94%20there%20was%20joy%20in%20the%20house%20hunt.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EMaybe%20you'd%20start%20by%20poking%20around%20Zillow%20before%20a%20Realtor%20friend%20hears%20you're%20in%20the%20market%20for%20a%20change%20of%20scenery.%20She%20might%20offer%20to%20spend%20her%20Sunday%20driving%20you%20around%20to%20a%20few%20homes.%20No%20pressure%2C%20she'd%20say%20%E2%80%94%20her%20services%20are%20free.%20You%20float%20through%20living%20rooms%20and%20bedrooms%2C%20orchestrating%20home%20makeovers%20in%20your%20head.%20Maybe%20you%20find%20a%20house%20you%20like%3B%20maybe%20you%20don't.%20That%20evening%2C%20you%20and%20your%20agent%20chat%20about%20next%20steps%20over%20a%20glass%20of%20wine.%20The%20headaches%20come%20later%3B%20at%20this%20point%2C%20it's%20all%20about%20possibilities.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAs%20of%20Saturday%2C%20those%20carefree%20days%20are%20gone.%20Now%2C%20before%20a%20real-estate%20agent%20so%20much%20as%20opens%20a%20door%20for%20you%2C%20they'll%20probably%20ask%20you%20to%20sign%20what's%20known%20as%20a%20buyer-representation%20agreement.%20The%20contract%20will%20lay%20out%20the%20terms%20of%20their%20services%20and%20how%20much%20they%20expect%20to%20be%20paid.%20This%20kind%20of%20agreement%20used%20to%20be%20optional%2C%20at%20least%20so%20early%20in%20the%20game%2C%20and%20most%20agents%20decided%20it%20wasn't%20worth%20the%20hassle.%20They%20reasoned%20that%20because%20of%20the%20way%20agents'%20commissions%20were%20structured%2C%20buyers%20didn't%20%3Cem%3Ereally%20%3C%2Fem%3Ehave%20to%20worry%20about%20those%20details%2C%20and%20they%20feared%20%E2%80%94%20maybe%20correctly%20%E2%80%94%20that%20the%20formality%20would%20scare%20off%20potential%20clients.%20Now%20they%20no%20longer%20have%20a%20choice.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20new%20rule%2C%20which%20is%20part%20of%20a%20sweeping%20legal%20settlement%2C%20promises%20to%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fhomebuyers-real-estate-revolution-nar-lawsuits-new-rules-realtors-agents-2024-4%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Efundamentally%20rewire%20the%20housing%20market%3C%2Fa%3E.%20It'll%20force%20buyers%20to%20think%20seriously%20about%20how%20their%20agents%20get%20paid%2C%20something%20they%20rarely%20had%20to%20consider%20in%20the%20past.%20Some%20buyers%20could%20find%20themselves%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fbad-real-estate-agents-realtors-homebuyers-sellers-housing-market-2023-7%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Elegally%20bound%20to%20a%20clumsy%20agent%3C%2Fa%3E%20or%20on%20the%20hook%20for%20thousands%20of%20dollars.%20Real-estate%20agents%2C%20on%20the%20other%20hand%2C%20may%20struggle%20to%20get%20would-be%20clients%20to%20sign%20on%20the%20dotted%20line.%20Those%20who%20can't%20%26quot%3Bcommunicate%20value%26quot%3B%20%E2%80%94%20a%20catchphrase%20among%20brokers%20that%20basically%20means%20%26quot%3Bconvince%20buyers%20that%20your%20services%20are%20worth%20a%20few%20months'%20pay%26quot%3B%20%E2%80%94%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Freal-estate-agents-realtors-reckoning-housing-market-home-sales-slow-2023-4%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Erisk%20flunking%20out%20of%20the%20business%3C%2Fa%3E.%20This%20may%20sound%20like%20a%20huge%20headache%20for%20both%20parties%2C%20but%20there%20are%20real%20upsides.%20Buyers%20may%20be%20more%20likely%20to%20vet%20their%20options%20before%20settling%20down%20with%20an%20agent%2C%20and%20many%20could%20actually%20spend%20less%20on%20commissions.%20Those%20who%20panic%20at%20the%20prospect%20of%20paying%20their%20agent%20out%20of%20pocket%20will%20almost%20certainly%20be%20able%20to%20find%20workarounds.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EOne%20thing%20is%20clear%3A%20Casual%20home%20shopping%20is%20a%20thing%20of%20the%20past.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BIt's%20a%20huge%20behavior%20change%20for%20Realtors%2C%26quot%3B%20Laura%20Ellis%2C%20an%20executive%20at%20Baird%20%26amp%3B%20Warner%2C%20a%20Chicago-area%20real-estate%20brokerage%2C%20told%20me%20recently.%20%26quot%3BIt's%20the%20biggest%20change%20in%20over%20100%20years.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Chr%3E%3Cp%3EHome%20sellers%20have%20always%20had%20to%20think%2C%20at%20least%20in%20passing%2C%20about%20agent%20commissions.%20The%20typical%20seller%20hires%20an%20agent%20who%20agrees%20to%20market%20the%20home%20in%20exchange%20for%20a%20cut%20of%20the%20sale%20price%20(usually%20between%205%25%20and%206%25).%20The%20seller's%20agent%20then%20lists%20the%20home%20on%20a%20multiple%20listing%20service%2C%20a%20local%20database%20where%20other%20agents%20can%20find%20details%20on%20homes%20for%20sale%2C%20and%20promises%20to%20split%20their%20commission%20with%20the%20buyer's%20agent.%20Let's%20say%20the%20seller%20brings%20in%20%24500%2C000%20from%20the%20deal.%20They'll%20hand%205%25%2C%20or%20%2425%2C000%2C%20to%20their%20agent%2C%20who%20then%20gives%20half%2C%20or%20%2412%2C500%2C%20to%20the%20buyer's%20agent.%20A%20buyer%20might%20stress%20over%20a%20down%20payment%20and%20grumble%20over%20shelling%20out%20a%20few%20thousand%20dollars%20for%20title%20insurance%2C%20but%20they%20never%20had%20to%20sweat%20the%20money%20changing%20hands%20between%20agents.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20power%20of%20the%20multiple%20listing%20service%20ensured%20the%20payments%20flowed%20this%20way.%20A%20seller's%20agent%20was%20required%20to%20offer%20%3Cem%3Esome%3C%2Fem%3E%20compensation%20to%20the%20buyer's%20agent%20when%20posting%20a%20home%20on%20the%20database%2C%20and%20while%20it%20could%20technically%20be%20as%20little%20as%20%241%2C%20most%20stuck%20with%20the%20status%20quo%20of%202.5%25%20to%203%25%20of%20the%20sale%20price.%20I've%20written%20a%20lot%20about%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Freal-estate-agents-lawsuits-buy-sell-homes-forever-housing-market-2023-6%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Ewhy%20the%20system%20worked%20this%20way%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20but%20the%20important%20thing%20to%20know%20is%20that%20it%20exposed%20the%20industry%20to%20all%20kinds%20of%20accusations.%20Critics%20complained%20that%20it%20made%20no%20sense%20for%20a%20seller%2C%20who%20hopes%20to%20collect%20the%20highest%20possible%20price%2C%20to%20funnel%20a%20percentage%20to%20the%20buyer's%20agent.%20They%20also%20feared%20that%20buyers'%20agents%20might%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Freal-estate-agent-commissions-steering-hiding-homes-housing-market-lawsuits-2024-3%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3E%26quot%3Bsteer%26quot%3B%20clients%20away%20from%20homes%3C%2Fa%3E%20that%20dared%20to%20offer%20less%20than%20the%20going%20rate.%20They%20argued%20that%20MLS%20rules%20discouraged%20negotiations%20and%20forced%20buyers%20and%20sellers%20to%20pay%20too%20much%20in%20commissions.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAt%20the%20center%20of%20this%20system%20was%20the%20National%20Association%20of%20Realtors%2C%20the%20powerful%20industry%20group%20that%20effectively%20controls%20about%2097%25%20of%20local%20multiple%20listing%20services%2C%20oversees%20roughly%201.5%20million%20agents%20who%20pay%20to%20be%20members%2C%20and%20pretty%20much%20sets%20the%20ground%20rules%20for%20buying%20and%20selling%20homes%20in%20America.%20A%20few%20years%20ago%2C%20a%20group%20of%20disgruntled%20sellers%20sued%20the%20NAR%2C%20claiming%20that%20they'd%20been%20strong-armed%20into%20paying%20the%20customary%205%25%20to%206%25%20of%20the%20sale%20price%20in%20commissions.%20Last%20October%2C%20the%20plaintiffs%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Flawsuits-verdict-realtors-brokerages-real-estate-agents-home-buying-selling-2023-11%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Escored%20a%20surprise%20victory%3C%2Fa%3E%20in%20the%20first%20case%20to%20reach%20trial.%20As%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Freal-estate-antitrust-lawsuits-verdict-agent-commissions-nar-future-homebuying-2023-12%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Emore%20suits%20piled%20up%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20it%20became%20clear%20that%20the%20NAR%20would%20need%20to%20cut%20a%20deal.%20In%20March%2C%20the%20organization%20agreed%20to%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fnational-association-realtors-lawsuit-settlement-housing-market-homebuying-agents-commissions-2024-3%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Epay%20%24418%20million%20to%20settle%3C%2Fa%3E.%20It%20also%20agreed%20to%20update%20the%20rules%20governing%20local%20multiple%20listing%20services%20and%20agents%20who%20use%20them.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThat%20brings%20us%20to%20Saturday%2C%20Aug.%2017.%20As%20of%20that%20date%2C%20agents%20can%20no%20longer%20advertise%20commissions%20on%20the%20MLS%2C%20which%20means%20the%20databases%20can%20no%20longer%20be%20used%20as%20a%20cudgel%20to%20make%20sure%20agents%20get%20paid%20the%20typical%20commission.%20The%20catch%20is%20that%20listing%20agents%20can%20still%20technically%20offer%20commissions%20to%20buyers'%20agents%20pretty%20much%20anywhere%20else%20%E2%80%94%20on%20their%20websites%2C%20over%20the%20phone%2C%20on%20billboards%20if%20they%20want%20to.%20This%20could%20allow%20for%20business%20as%20usual%3A%20A%20listing%20agent%20might%20still%20offer%20to%20split%20a%20commission%20with%20the%20buyer's%20agent%20through%20any%20of%20these%20alternate%20avenues.%20But%20in%20order%20to%20keep%20using%20the%20MLS%2C%20buyers'%20agents%20will%20have%20to%20abide%20by%20another%20rule%20that%20will%20further%20upend%20the%20old%20way%20of%20doing%20things.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EBefore%20they%20can%20even%20tour%20a%20home%20with%20a%20client%2C%20any%20agent%20who%20uses%20a%20Realtor-controlled%20MLS%20%E2%80%94%20which%2C%20again%2C%20is%20most%20of%20them%20%E2%80%94%20will%20have%20to%20get%20the%20client%20to%20sign%20an%20agreement%20that%20spells%20out%20a%20few%20things.%20First%2C%20the%20agent%20will%20have%20to%20say%20how%20much%20they%20expect%20to%20be%20paid.%20This%20could%20be%20a%20percentage%20of%20the%20purchase%20price%2C%20like%202.5%25%2C%20but%20it%20could%20also%20be%20a%20flat%20fee%20or%20even%20an%20hourly%20rate.%20It%20just%20has%20to%20be%20a%20clear%20amount%2C%20not%20contingent%20on%20what%20the%20seller%20is%20offering.%20And%20unless%20both%20sides%20agree%20to%20amend%20the%20contract%2C%20the%20buyer's%20agent%20can't%20receive%20more%20than%20that%20amount%20down%20the%20line%3B%20if%20a%20seller%20offers%203%25%20but%20the%20buyer's%20agent%20agrees%20to%20only%202.5%25%2C%20the%20buyer's%20rep%20has%20to%20either%20turn%20down%20that%20extra%20money%20or%20pass%20it%20along%20to%20their%20client.%20The%20NAR%20has%20maintained%20that%20buyers%20were%20free%20to%20negotiate%20commissions%20even%20before%20the%20lawsuits.%20But%20now%20that's%20much%20more%20likely%20to%20happen.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAgain%2C%20a%20seller%20may%20still%20offer%20to%20pay%20the%20commission%20of%20the%20buyer's%20agent%20as%20long%20as%20that%20offer%20is%20not%20made%20through%20the%20MLS.%20But%20they%20may%20choose%20not%20to%20offer%20anything%20at%20all%2C%20an%20option%20that%20could%20work%20out%20well%20for%20both%20parties.%20That's%20because%20buyers%2C%20in%20their%20offers%20to%20sellers%2C%20can%20ask%20to%20get%20some%20money%20back%20so%20they%20can%20pay%20their%20agent%20directly.%20This%20is%20what's%20known%20as%20a%20seller%20credit%2C%20and%20the%20nonprofit%20Consumer%20Advocates%20in%20American%20Real%20Estate%20recommends%20that%20buyers%20ask%20for%20it%20if%20they%20don't%20want%20to%20pay%20their%20agent%20out%20of%20pocket.%20Sellers%20may%20agree%20to%20it%20in%20the%20interest%20of%20getting%20a%20deal%20done%2C%20especially%20since%20it%20could%20result%20in%20savings%20for%20both%20sides.%20In%20the%20old%20days%2C%20a%20seller%20might%20have%20unthinkingly%20offered%20a%20commission%20of%202%25%20or%20even%203%25%20to%20the%20buyer's%20agent.%20But%20if%20you%2C%20as%20a%20buyer%2C%20negotiate%20a%20fee%20for%20your%20agent%20of%20only%201%25%2C%20you're%20basically%20saving%20the%20seller%20%E2%80%94%20and%20yourself%20%E2%80%94%20money.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EBut%20these%20workarounds%20are%20by%20no%20means%20guaranteed%2C%20especially%20in%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fhottest-states-to-buy-property-in-right-now-housing-biggerpockets-2024-8%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Ehot%20real-estate%20markets%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20and%20some%20in%20the%20industry%20fear%20that%20the%20quick%20fix%20of%20advertising%20commissions%20outside%20the%20MLS%20could%20open%20them%20up%20to%20more%20legal%20trouble%20down%20the%20line.%20In%20the%20meantime%2C%20more%20buyers%20may%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fnew-rule-of-home-buying-fire-your-real-estate-agent-2024-4%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Echoose%20to%20forgo%20an%20agent%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20work%20out%20an%20alternative%20payment%20structure%2C%20or%20accept%20that%20they%20may%20have%20to%20fork%20over%20money%20to%20cover%20the%20gap%20between%20what%20they%20agreed%20to%20pay%20their%20agent%20and%20whatever%20the%20seller%20is%20willing%20to%20contribute.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EOther%20terms%20of%20the%20agreement%20will%20also%20be%20up%20to%20the%20buyer%20and%20their%20agent.%20They%20can%20decide%20which%20services%20the%20agent%20will%20provide%20and%20for%20how%20long%3B%20whether%20they%20want%20to%20maintain%20an%20exclusive%20relationship%20or%20allow%20the%20buyer%20to%20work%20with%20other%20agents%3B%20what%20to%20do%20if%20the%20arrangement%20sours%20and%20one%20party%20wants%20to%20walk%20away.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20basic%20terms%20of%20a%20buyer-representation%20agreement%20should%2C%20in%20theory%2C%20be%20fairly%20simple%20to%20spell%20out%3A%20How%20much%20is%20the%20buyer%20going%20to%20pay%2C%20and%20for%20which%20services%3F%20But%20as%20with%20all%20modern%20contracts%2C%20there%20are%20complications.%20The%20Consumer%20Federation%20of%20America%20has%20raised%20concerns%20about%20the%20standard%20forms%20promoted%20by%20some%20state%20Realtor%20associations%2C%20saying%20even%20lawyers%20might%20struggle%20to%20parse%20the%20tiny%20typeface%20and%20thick%20legalese.%20It%20has%20argued%20that%20buyers%20risk%20agreeing%20to%20unnecessary%20fees%20or%20finding%20themselves%20legally%20bound%20to%20an%20agent%20who%20turns%20out%20to%20be%20a%20dud.%20After%20the%20California%20Association%20of%20Realtors%2C%20which%20has%20more%20than%20180%2C000%20members%2C%20unveiled%20a%20draft%20of%20its%20standard%20form%2C%20the%20CFA%20released%20a%20report%20written%20by%20Tanya%20Monestier%2C%20a%20professor%20of%20contract%20law%20at%20the%20University%20at%20Buffalo%2C%20that%20lambasted%20the%20draft%20as%20%26quot%3Bvirtually%20unreadable.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ETake%2C%20for%20instance%2C%20this%20section%2C%20which%20is%20meant%20to%20explain%20what%20happens%20if%20the%20same%20agent%20represents%20both%20the%20buyer%20and%20the%20seller%3A%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BACCOUNTING%20FOR%20PAYMENTS%20TO%20BROKER%20IF%20BROKER%20ALSO%20REPRESENTS%20SELLER%3A%20Notwithstanding%20paragraph%202D(2)%2C%20if%20Broker%20has%20a%20listing%20agreement%20with%20the%20seller%20of%20the%20property%20to%20be%20purchased%2C%20no%20credit%20toward%20Buyer's%20compensation%20obligation%20shall%20be%20given%20for%20the%20amount%20due%20Broker%20by%20seller%20for%20the%20compensation%20Broker%20is%20owed%20as%20the%20seller's%20agent.%20Buyer%20will%20pay%20the%20amount%20in%20paragraph%202D(1)%2C%20less%20any%20amount%20offered%20by%20Broker%20to%20buyer's%20agents.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EImagine%204%2C000%20words%20of%20that.%20A%20tiny%20section%20that%20basically%20says%20%26quot%3BThe%20buyer%20and%20the%20seller%20will%20each%20have%20to%20pay%20the%20agent%20separately%26quot%3B%20turns%20into%20word%20vomit.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BNo%20buyer%20will%20understand%20this%20provision's%20meaning%2C%26quot%3B%20Monestier%20wrote.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20California%20association%20did%20end%20up%20making%20substantive%20revisions%2C%20and%20said%20in%20a%20statement%20that%20%26quot%3Bthe%20complexity%20of%20the%20agreement%20reflects%20the%20complexity%20of%20California%20real%20estate%20transactions.%26quot%3B%20But%20the%20form%20is%20%26quot%3Bstill%20very%20lengthy%2C%26quot%3B%20Monestier%20told%20me%20recently.%20%26quot%3BIt's%20still%20very%20hard%20to%20slog%20through.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Chr%3E%3Cp%3EConsumers%20may%2C%20understandably%2C%20be%20wary%20of%20signing%20a%20complex%20contract%20so%20early%20in%20the%20process%2C%20but%20the%20new%20setup%20has%20benefits.%20Sellers%20often%20interview%20several%20agents%20before%20picking%20the%20one%20who%20seems%20like%20they'll%20reel%20in%20the%20most%20lucrative%20offers.%20Buyers%20should%20similarly%20vet%20agents%20with%20an%20eye%20toward%20the%20bottom%20line.%20After%20all%2C%20internet-savvy%20buyers%20don't%20need%20agents'%20help%20to%20find%20houses%20anymore%2C%20Ellis%2C%20the%20brokerage%20executive%20in%20Chicago%2C%20told%20me.%20But%20they%20probably%20still%20want%20someone%20to%20hold%20their%20hand%20through%20the%20rest%20of%20the%20process.%20And%20if%20you're%20a%20buyer%20who%20just%20wants%20someone%20to%20open%20doors%20for%20you%20to%20get%20a%20sense%20of%20what's%20out%20there%2C%20Monestier%20said%2C%20you%20can%20hold%20off%20on%20signing%20with%20an%20agent%20and%20deal%20directly%20with%20sellers'%20agents.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EUltimately%2C%20this%20is%20about%20ensuring%20that%20both%20a%20buyer%20and%20their%20agent%20enter%20the%20relationship%20with%20a%20clear%20understanding%20of%20what%20they'll%20get%20out%20of%20it.%20A%20buyer%2C%20Ellis%20said%2C%20might%20want%20to%20ask%20a%20prospective%20agent%3A%20%26quot%3BIf%20I%20work%20with%20you%2C%20how%20are%20you%20going%20to%20get%20me%20the%20house%20that%20I%20want%2C%20the%20terms%20I%20want%3F%20How%20are%20you%20going%20to%20get%20me%20through%20this%20transaction%20as%20smoothly%20as%20possible%3F%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20idea%20that%20sellers%20pay%20both%20agents'%20commissions%20has%20always%20been%20a%20clever%20sleight%20of%20hand.%20Buyer-representation%20agreements%20may%20be%20thorny%2C%20but%20at%20least%20they'll%20make%20it%20impossible%20for%20buyers%20to%20ignore%20the%20costs%20of%20using%20an%20agent.%20Real-estate%20agents%2C%20like%20people%20in%20any%20other%20job%2C%20provide%20a%20service.%20And%20nobody%20works%20for%20free.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Chr%3E%3Cp%3E%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fauthor%2Fjames-rodriguez%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3E%3Cem%3E%3Cu%3EJames%20Rodriguez%3C%2Fu%3E%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%3Cem%3E%20is%20a%20senior%20reporter%20on%20Business%20Insider's%20Discourse%20team.%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cdiv%3ERead%20the%20original%20article%20on%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fnew-homebuying-rule-sign-buyer-representation-agreement-realtors-lawsuit-settlement-2024-8%5C%22%3EBusiness%20Insider%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1724060222000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F66bf662db4912df3ae1c4b1d%3Fformat%3Djpeg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fnew-homebuying-rule-sign-buyer-representation-agreement-realtors-lawsuit-settlement-2024-8%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22New%20rules%20for%20Realtors%20will%20make%20buying%20a%20home%20more%20complicated.%20But%20both%20buyers%20and%20sellers%20could%20save%20a%20ton%20of%20money.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22jrodriguez%40insider.com%20(James%20Rodriguez)%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A9%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fnew-homebuying-rule-sign-buyer-representation-agreement-realtors-lawsuit-settlement-2024-8%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Bangladesh%20Polls%20To%20Be%20Delayed%3F%20Muhammad%20Yunus%20Cites%20Need%20For%20Key%20Reforms%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cp%3EIn%20a%20key%20address%20to%20diplomats%20in%20Dhaka%20on%20Sunday%2C%20Muhammad%20Yunus%2C%20the%20Chief%20Adviser%20to%20Bangladesh's%20interim%20government%2C%20called%20for%20comprehensive%20reforms%20before%20holding%20the%20next%20general%20elections.%20This%20meeting%20marked%20Mr%20Yunus'%20first%20engagement%20with%20the%20diplomatic%20community%20since%20assuming%20office%20on%20August%208%2C%20following%20the%20resignation%20of%20former%20Prime%20Minister%20Sheikh%20Hasina.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMr%20Yunus%2C%20a%20Nobel%20laureate%2C%20took%20charge%20amid%20a%20volatile%20political%20landscape%20that%20saw%20mass%20protests%20and%20violence%20resulting%20in%20the%20ousting%20of%20Ms%20Hasina.%20In%20his%20address%2C%20Yunus%20outlined%20the%20interim%20government's%20roadmap%20for%20a%20stable%20and%20democratic%20Bangladesh%2C%20starting%20with%20a%20free%2C%20fair%2C%20and%20participatory%20election.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BWe%20will%20hold%20a%20free%2C%20fair%20participatory%20election%20as%20soon%20as%20we%20can%20complete%20our%20mandate%20to%20carry%20out%20vital%20reforms%20in%20our%20election%20commission%2C%20judiciary%2C%20civil%20administration%2C%20security%20forces%20and%20media%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20told%20diplomats%2C%20including%20India's%20High%20Commissioner%20in%20Dhaka%2C%20Pranay%20Verma.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch3%3E%3Cstrong%3ERestoring%20Normalcy%C2%A0%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh3%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EOn%20August%205%2C%20Ms%20Hasina%2C%20aged%2076%2C%20fled%20Bangladesh%20by%20helicopter%20to%20India%20as%20protesters%20overran%20the%20streets%20of%20Dhaka.%20Her%2015-year%20rule%2C%20marked%20by%20allegations%20of%20human%20rights%20abuses%2C%20came%20to%20a%20dramatic%20end.%20The%20weeks%20leading%20up%20to%20her%20ousting%20were%20bloody%2C%20with%20more%20than%20450%20dying%20during%20the%20unrest%20and%20several%20reports%20of%20attacks%20on%20Bangladesh's%20Hindu%20minority%20community.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20Chief%20Adviser%20said%20restoring%20law%20and%20order%20in%20the%20country%20is%20a%20top%20priority%20for%20his%20government.%20%26quot%3BWe%20will%20be%20close%20to%20normalcy%20within%20a%20short%20period%2C%20with%20the%20unwavering%20support%20of%20our%20people%20and%20patriotic%20armed%20forces%2C%26quot%3B%20Mr%20Yunus%20said.%20%26quot%3BThe%20top%20priority%20of%20the%20Interim%20Government%20would%20be%20to%20bring%20the%20law%20and%20order%20situation%20under%20control...The%20armed%20forces%20will%20continue%20to%20serve%20in%20aid%20of%20civil%20power%20as%20long%20as%20the%20situation%20warrants.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch3%3E%3Cstrong%3EReviving%20Economy%C2%A0%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh3%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20addition%20to%20political%20reforms%2C%20Mr%20Yunus%20spoke%20about%20the%20need%20for%20robust%20economic%20reforms.%20The%20country%20had%20suffered%20under%20what%20he%20described%20as%20Ms%20Hasina's%20%26quot%3Bbrutal%20dictatorship%2C%26quot%3B%20which%2C%20according%20to%20Mr%20Yunus%2C%20had%20led%20to%20widespread%20corruption%20and%20mismanagement.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BOur%20government%20will%20undertake%20far-reaching%20economic%20reforms%20to%20restore%20macroeconomic%20stability%20and%20sustain%20growth%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMr%20Yunus%20accused%20Sheikh%20Hasina%20of%20systematically%20destroying%20the%20country's%20institutions%20during%20her%2015-year%20tenure.%20He%20alleged%20that%20elections%20under%20Ms%20Hasina's%20rule%20were%20rigged%2C%20and%20democratic%20rights%20were%20suppressed.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BIn%20their%20efforts%20to%20stay%20in%20power%2C%20Sheikh%20Hasina's%20dictatorship%20destroyed%20every%20institution%20of%20the%20country%2C%26quot%3B%20Mr%20Yunus%20said.%20He%20described%20the%20judiciary%20as%20broken%20and%20accused%20the%20former%20administration%20of%20allowing%20political%20patronage%20to%20rob%20banks%20and%20plunder%20the%20state%20coffers.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20Nobel%20laureate%20described%20the%20recent%20mass%20uprising%20as%20a%20%26quot%3BSecond%20Revolution%2C%26quot%3B%20led%20by%20students%20and%20ordinary%20citizens%20who%20sought%20to%20reclaim%20their%20democratic%20rights.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch3%3E%3Cstrong%3EInternational%20Support%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh3%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20his%20message%20to%20the%20international%20community%2C%20Mr%20Yunus%20called%20for%20continued%20support%20in%20rebuilding%20Bangladesh%20and%20transitioning%20to%20a%20fully%20functional%20democracy.%20He%20assured%20the%20diplomats%20that%20Bangladesh%20would%20maintain%20its%20role%20as%20a%20proponent%20of%20multilateralism%2C%20with%20the%20United%20Nations%20at%20the%20core%20of%20its%20foreign%20policy.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BWe%20believe%20all%20our%20friends%20and%20partners%20in%20the%20international%20community%20will%20stand%20by%20our%20government%20and%20people%20as%20we%20chart%20a%20new%20democratic%20future%2C%26quot%3B%20Yunus%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BBangladesh%20stands%20at%20the%20crossroads%20of%20a%20new%20beginning.%20Our%20valiant%20students%20and%20people%20deserve%20a%20lasting%20transformation%20of%20our%20nation.%20It%20is%20a%20difficult%20journey%20and%20we%20need%20your%20help%20along%20the%20way.%20We%20need%20to%20fulfil%20their%20aspirations.%20The%20sooner%20the%20better%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20added.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMr%20Yunus%20also%20welcomed%20the%20United%20Nations'%20decision%20to%20send%20a%20fact-finding%20mission%20to%20investigate%20the%20recent%20violence%2C%20committing%20to%20cooperate%20fully%20with%20the%20international%20inquiry.%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1724060160000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2024-08%2Fj4vjvr9g_muhammad-yunus-afp_625x300_19_August_24.jpeg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Fworld-news%2Fmuhammad-yunus-message-to-diplomats-big-reforms-ahead-of-bangladesh-polls-6370076%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22In%20a%20key%20address%20to%20diplomats%20in%20Dhaka%20on%20Sunday%2C%20Muhammad%20Yunus%2C%20the%20Chief%20Adviser%20to%20Bangladesh's%20interim%20government%2C%20called%20for%20comprehensive%20reforms%20before%20holding%20the%20next%20general%20elections.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Fworld-news%2Fmuhammad-yunus-message-to-diplomats-big-reforms-ahead-of-bangladesh-polls-6370076%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Harvey%20Keitel%2C%20Britt%20Robertson%20Team%20for%20Comedy-Drama%20%E2%80%98The%20Letter%E2%80%99%20From%20Director%20Rodrigo%20H.%20Vila%20(EXCLUSIVE)%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%22%2C%22published%22%3A1724060037000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22