ver%2C%20a%20new%20California%20law%20could%20change%20the%20course%20of%20the%20AI%20revolution%20forever.%3C%2Fli%3E%3Cli%3ETech%20giants%20like%20Meta%20and%20OpenAI%20argue%20the%20bill%20would%20stifle%20AI%20innovation.%3C%2Fli%3E%3C%2Ful%3E%3Cp%3ESilicon%20Valley%20is%20divided%20over%20a%20landmark%20bill%20in%20California%20that%20could%20radically%20change%20the%20pace%20of%20AI%20development%20everywhere.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ECalifornia%20Sen.%20Scott%20Wiener%20introduced%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fleginfo.legislature.ca.gov%2Ffaces%2FbillNavClient.xhtml%3Fbill_id%3D202320240SB1047%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3E%3Cspan%3ESB%201047%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%3Cspan%3E%C2%A0in%20February%2C%3C%2Fspan%3E%20and%20it%20has%20since%20won%20support%20from%20legislators%20on%20both%20sides%20of%20the%20aisle.%20%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIt%20passed%20the%20Senate's%20Committee%20on%20Privacy%20and%20Consumer%20Protection%20in%20June%20and%20the%20Assembly's%20Appropriations%20Committee%20last%3Cstrong%3E%20%3C%2Fstrong%3Eweek.%20The%20full%20Assembly%20is%20scheduled%20to%20vote%20on%20the%20bill%20by%20the%20end%20of%20the%20month.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ECalifornia%20has%20established%20itself%20as%20a%20leader%20in%20the%20global%20AI%20arms%20race%2C%20with%2035%20of%20the%20top%2050%20AI%20companies%20based%20in%20the%20state%2C%20according%20to%20a%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.brookings.edu%2Farticles%2Fcalifornia-charts-the-future-of-ai%2F%23%3A~%3Atext%3DThe%2520executive%2520order%2520notes%2520that%2Cresponsible%2520AI%2520policies%2520and%2520regulations.%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Ereport%20from%20the%20Brookings%20Institute%3C%2Fa%3E.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ECalifornia%20Gov.%20Gavin%20Newsom%20has%20worked%20to%20help%20further%20his%20state's%20status%20as%20a%20global%20AI%20pioneer.%20Earlier%20this%20year%2C%20California%20revealed%20a%20state%20worker%20training%20program%2C%20held%20a%20generative%20AI%20summit%2C%20and%20launched%20pilot