d%20out%20to%20me%20begging%20for%20programming%20advice%20and%20praising%20my%20expertise%20%E2%80%94%C2%A0which%20was%20too%20little%2C%20too%20late.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EUnfortunately%2C%20a%20lot%20of%20my%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fdating-silicon-valley-big-tech-hard-want-marriage-kids-2024-7%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Efemale%20friends%20in%20tech%3C%2Fa%3E%20can%20relate.%20I've%20heard%20multiple%20instances%20of%20men%20quizzing%20my%20friends%20on%20dates%20as%20a%20%26quot%3Bjoke%2C%26quot%3B%20but%20it%20comes%20across%20as%20a%20serious%20dismissal%20of%20their%20intelligence.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%22af57dbd0-2235-4317-9599-c8c89a2b4a0a%5C%22%3EI'm%20not%20your%20dream%20girl%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20opposite%20side%20of%20the%20coin%20is%20men%20who%20get%20a%20little%20too%20excited%20about%20the%20idea%20of%20dating%20a%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fleading-women-in-tech-discuss-how-women-are-transforming-the-industry-2023-3%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Ewoman%20in%20tech%3C%2Fa%3E%20and%20treat%20me%20like%20their%20manic%20pixie%20dream%20girl.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20term%20usually%20describes%20quirky%2C%20fictional%20female%20characters%20who%20%26quot%3Btransform%20a%20man%20through%20whimsical%20means%2C%26quot%3B%20so%20I%20never%20thought%20it%20could%20apply%20to%20me.%20But%2C%20one%20guy%20in%20college%20and%20several%20men%20on%20dating%20apps%20have%20referred%20to%20me%20as%20one.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EI%20hate%20that%20the%20term%20centers%20on%20men%20when%20my%20quirks%20are%20my%20genuine%20way%20of%20navigating%20the%20world.%20I'm%20bubbly%20and%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fhow-adult-adhd-autism-diagnosis-changed-life-neurodivergent-2023-12%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Eneurodivergent%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20with%20a%20colorful%20sense%20of%20fashion%20and%20nerdy%20interests%2C%20and%20none%20of%20those%20qualities%20are%20put%20on%20for%20men.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%224c6d733f-d3e0-4353-b86c-1c2ce138e9ab%5C%22%3EI%20don't%20like%20being%20treated%20like%20a%20rare%20gem%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EI%20briefly%20went%20out%20with%20this%20guy%20who%20treated%20me%20like%20I%20was%20some%20rare%20gem.%20He%20would%20pick%20my%20brain%20and%20marvel%20at%20my%20(arguably%20generic)%20responses.%20For%20example%2C%20he%20asked%20me%20my%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fbaskin-robbins-ice-cream-flavors-ranked-worst-to-best-review%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Efavorite%20ice%20cream%20flavor%3C%2Fa%3E%20and%20I%20think%20I%20said%20mint%20chip.%20He%20stared%20at%20me%20in%20awe%20as%20he%20remarked%20how%20unique%20and%20different%20I%20was%20from%20other%20girls.%20It%20was%20ridiculous.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EWe%20kept%20dating%20for%20a%20few%20weeks%20despite%20being%20put%20off%20by%20his%20enthusiasm%2C%20but%20things%20reached%20a%20head%20when%20I%20told%20him%20I%20had%20landed%20a%20new%20job%20at%20a%20financial%20institution.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EHe%20was%20beside%20himself%20and%20told%20me%20he%20was%20upset%20I%20wasn't%20pursuing%20my%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fi-work-8-to-5-job-to-supplement-esports-career-2024-4%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3E%26quot%3Bdream%26quot%3B%20of%20gaming%3C%2Fa%3E.%20Sure%2C%20I%20enjoyed%20gaming%2C%20but%20I%20never%20said%20it%20was%20my%20dream.%20I%20was%20young%20and%20uncomfortable%20and%20laughed%20it%20off%2C%20telling%20him%20I%20just%20needed%20a%20job%20to%20pay%20my%20bills.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EHe%20seemed%20extremely%20disappointed%20that%20I%20didn't%20fit%20this%20nerdy%20gamer%20girl%20aesthetic%20he%20envisioned.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%226da1ad0f-2916-4bea-8b87-10518d0a51e9%5C%22%3EI'm%20no%20longer%20settling%20for%20men%20who%20don't%20accept%20all%20of%20me%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EI%20want%20to%20clarify%20that%20not%20every%20man%20I've%20dated%2