25%20in%202023%2C%20while%20management%20fees%20bumped%20up%20to%201.54%25%20from%201.46%25.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ELike%20any%20industry%2C%20it%20was%20a%20function%20of%20supply%20and%20demand.%20Thanks%20to%20the%20stability%20many%20top%20multistrategy%20hedge%20funds%20displayed%20during%20the%20onset%20of%20the%20pandemic%2C%20LPs%20scrambled%20to%20get%20in.%20These%20sprawling%20managers%2C%20though%2C%20are%20the%20most%20expensive%20type%20of%20hedge%20fund%2C%20with%20much%20higher%20headcounts%20and%20more%20complicated%20systems%20than%20peers%20that%20focus%20solely%20on%20equity%20trading%20or%20macro%20investing.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThese%20funds%20used%20this%20demand%20to%20lock%20investors%20into%20high-fee%20agreements%2C%20but%20as%20interest%20rates%20have%20risen%20without%20a%20corresponding%20bump%20in%20returns%2C%20many%20allocators%20are%20wondering%20what%20they're%20paying%20for.%20Hedge-fund%20allocator%20Aurum%20found%20that%20multistrategy%20funds%20were%20up%2C%20on%20average%2C%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.aurum.com%2Fhedge-fund-data%2Fhedge-fund-industry-deep-dive%2Fhedge-fund-industry-performance-deep-dive-h1-2024%2F%23%3A~%3Atext%3DThe%2520hedge%2520fund%2520industry%2520was%2Creturned%25204.5%2525%2520for%2520the%2520year.%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3E6.1%25%20in%20the%20first%20half%3C%2Fa%3E%20of%202024%20%E2%80%94%20trailing%20the%20average%20quant-only%20fund%20and%20the%20S%26amp%3BP%20500's%20return%20of%2015%25%20over%20the%20same%20period.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ESome%20of%20the%20largest%20institutional%20investors%2C%20led%20by%20the%20%24200%20billion%20pension%20Teacher%20Retirement%20System%20of%20Texas%2C%20have%20gone%20so%20far%20as%20to%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.pionline.com%2Fhedge-funds%2Fpension-funds-consultants-press-cash-hurdles-hedge-fund-fee-arrangements%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Epublish%20an%20open%20letter%20to%20the%20industry%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20calling%20for%20managers%20to%20adopt%20a%20cash%20hurdle%20that%20would%20prevent%20them%20from%20receiving%20performance%20fees%20above%20what%20US%20treasury%20bonds%20would%20return.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20industry%20has%20%26quot%3Bgone%20full%20circle%26quot%3B%20on%20fees%2C%20said%20Lilly%20Knight%2C%20cohead%20of%20investment%20management%20at%20Franklin%20Templeton's%20K2%20Advisors%2C%20a%20%2410.2%20billion%20fund%20of%20hedge%20funds%2C%20and%20frustration%20is%20mounting.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EK2%2C%20she%20said%2C%20%26quot%3Bhas%20gently%20walked%20away%20from%20a%20few%20multistrats%2C%20reduced%20our%20allocations.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ELPs%20are%20paying%20not%20for%20performance%20but%20for%20the%20ongoing%20talent%20war%2C%20which%20has%20led%20to%20in-demand%20portfolio%20managers%20receiving%20eight-figure%20guaranteed%20payouts.%20While%20the%20structure%20of%20multistrategy%20firms%20%E2%80%94%20which%20combines%20teams%20trading%20different%20asset%20classes%20in%20many%20geographies%20to%20generate%20stable%20returns%20that%20are%20uncorrelated%20to%20the%20markets%20%E2%80%94%20is%20still%20beloved%2C%20the%20space%20has%20gotten%20so%20crowded%20that%20there's%20not%20enough%20talent%20to%20fill%20seats.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThis%20shortage%20is%20pushing%20the%20industry%20to%20a%20breaking%20point.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%222b705c7a-1dbc-4543-a7ae-e7f0bb7bfb65%5C%22%3E%3Cstrong%3EPeople%20problems%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EMany%20funds%20hoping%20to%20keep%20or%20attract%20top%20talent%20have%20resorted%20to%20charging%20%E2%80%94%20on%20top%20of%20a%20management%20fee%2C%20a%20performance%20charge%2C%20and%20a%20pass-through%20expense%20%E2%80%94%20a%20fixed%20fee%20that%20creates%20a%20pool%20of%20money%20just%20for%20paying%20PMs%2C%20Knight%20said.%20This%20new%20structure%2C%20which%20Knight%20said%20many%20funds%20rolled%20out%20in%20the%20last%2012%20months%2C%20is%20a%20break%20from%20the%20traditional%20model.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EKnight%20declined%20to%20name%20specific%20funds%20that%20have%20introduced%20this%20new%20charge%2C%20but%20known%20examples%20include%20managers%20such%20as%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fmarshall-wace-culture-split-between-recruits-and-old-guard-2024-5%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3ELondon-based%20Marshall%20Wace%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20which%20introduced%20a%2075-basis-point%20fee%20just%20for%20talent.%20While%20such%20measures%20seem%20extreme%20for%20some%20allocators%2C%20it's%20clear%20the%20industry's%20talent%20shortage%20isn't%20going%20away%20anytime%20soon.%20For%20example%2C%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fbalyasny-trims-asia-equity-head-archana-parekh-book-lead-buildout-2024-7%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3E%20in%20rebuilding%20its%20equities%20franchise%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20Balyasny%20has%20doled%20out%20more%20than%20%24200%20million%2C%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.bloomberg.com%2Fnews%2Farticles%2F2024-08-08%2Fbalyasny-goes-on-new-hiring-spree-with-200-million-in-payouts%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EBloomberg%20reported.%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIn%20the%20past%2C%20Knight%20said%2C%20the%20management%20fee%20was%20used%20to%20run%20the%20business%2C%20while%20the%20performance%20fee%20was%20used%20to%20%26quot%3Bpay%20the%20people.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BWasn't%20that%20enough%3F%26quot%3B%20she%20asked.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EA%20fixed%20fee%20turns%20that%20notion%20on%20its%20head%20because%20it%20guarantees%20payouts%20to%20investors%20who%20might%20not%20end%20up%20making%20any%20money.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BYou%20want%20people%20to%20be%20rewarded%20after%20the%20fact%2C%26quot%3B%20she%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%22d2077a72-aa97-4af5-9b17-254715a76c27%5C%22%3E%3Cstrong%3EInsulated%20at%20the%20top%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3ELike%20most%20industries%2C%20top%20hedge%20funds%20like%20Millennium%20and%20Citadel%20are%20not%20feeling%20the%20heat%20as%20intensely%20on%20fees%20as%20the%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fhow-multi-strategy-firms-are-balancing-growth-investor-demand-2023-12%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Espace's%20middle%20class%3C%2Fa%3E.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThere's%20still%20demand%20for%20the%20top%20tier%20of%20the%20industry%2C%20regardless%20of%20fees%2C%20according%20to%20James%20Ouderkirk%2C%20director%20of%20business%20development%20at%20GLASfunds%2C%20a%20%243%20billion%20alternatives%20platform%20that%20works%20with%20advisors%20for%20the%20wealthy.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThey%20understand%20that%20the%20returns%20have%20been%20there%26quot%3B%20at%20those%20managers%2C%20Ouderkirk%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThe%20fee%20pressures%20there%20are%20just%20not%20felt.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ECurrently%2C%20his%20platform%20recommends%20four%20different%20multistrategy%20options%20to%20its%20clients%2C%20including%20Morgan%20Stanley's%20Riverview%20Omni.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ELesser-known%20multi-managers%20and%20new%20launches%2C%20though%2C%20are%20getting%20pushback.%20Even%20with%20Bobby%20Jain's%20pedigree%2C%20his%20new%20firm%20launched%20in%20July%20with%20%245.3%20billion%20%E2%80%94%20less%20than%20many%20thought%20he%20would%20raise.%20Three%20people%20said%20that%20if%20Jain%20Global%20had%20launched%20five%20years%20earlier%2C%20it%20would%20have%20matched%20the%20%248.6%20billion%20haul%20Michael%20Gelband's%20ExodusPoint%20pulled%20in.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ESome%20managers%20have%20found%20ways%20to%20keep%20talent%20costs%20down.%20Norias%20Research%2C%20from%20former%20Point72%20president%20Doug%20Haynes%2C%20garnered%20interest%20from%20LPs%20because%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fnorias-research-launch-strategy-fees-2024-2%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Eit%20didn't%20have%20a%20pass-through%20fee%3C%2Fa%3E%20thanks%20to%20its%20quantamental%20structure.%20Systemic-trading%20funds%20such%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fcenterbook-partners-hedge-fund-using-other-firms-to-invest-2024-1%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Eas%20CenterBook%20Partners%3C%2Fa%3E%20pull%20investment%20data%20from%20dozens%20of%20partner%20funds%20that%20get%20a%20portion%20of%20the%20firm's%20performance%20fees%20but%20don't%20have%20to%20hire%20scores%20of%20individual%20PMs%20to%20get%20a%20diversified%20return%20stream.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAt%20Acadian%20Asset%20Management%2C%20the%20Boston-based%20firm%20launched%20its%20multistrategy%20hedge%20fund%204.5%20years%20ago%20with%20no%20gates%2C%20no%20lock-ups%2C%20and%20no%20pass-through%20fees.%20It%20offers%20monthly%20liquidity%20to%20its%20investors%2C%20according%20to%20Mike%20Gleason%2C%20the%20firm's%20director%20of%20equity%20alternative%20strategies.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20firm%20has%20been%20focused%20on%20keeping%20costs%20down%20for%20the%20strategy%2C%20Gleason%20said%2C%20and%20is%20very%20intentional%20about%20adding%20new%20strategies%20to%20the%20fund%20%E2%80%94%20never%20planning%20to%20exceed%20a%20dozen%20or%20so%20total.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BWe%20are%20building%20them%20in%20a%20very%20purposeful%20way%20to%20fit%20them%20together%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EBeing%20very%20particular%20about%20what%20strategies%20it%20adds%20helps%20the%20fund%20control%20costs%20by%20keeping%20its%20head%20count%20down%20%E2%80%94%20and%20not%20competing%20for%20the%20same%20talent%20as%20the%20largest%20managers.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BIf%20you%20can%20control%20the%20costs%2C%20you%20can%20recapture%20some%20of%20that%20alpha%2C%26quot%3B%20Gleason%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%22104e4d0c-caa4-41fb-9837-9fccac8aa9ea%5C%22%3E%3Cstrong%3EWho%20should%20be%20paid%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EFund-of-funds%20Corbin%20Capital%20isn't%20an%20investor%20in%20the%20biggest%20platforms%20in%20the%20world%2C%20partly%20because%20they're%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fhedge-fund-allocators-due-diligence-multi-strategy-firms-2024-2%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3E%20%26quot%3Bso%20hard%20to%20evaluate%2C%26quot%3B%20%3C%2Fa%3Eaccording%20to%20Craig%20Bergstrom%2C%20the%20firm's%20chief%20investment%20officer.%20But%20generally%2C%20he%20said%2C%20fees%20in%20the%20industry%20are%20too%20elevated%20for%20the%20current%20market%20reality.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EDecades%20ago%2C%20at%20the%20start%20of%20the%20industry%2C%20the%20best%20hedge%20funds%20could%20truly%20outperform%20thanks%20to%20higher%20volatility%20and%20less%20competition.%20This%20isn't%20the%20case%20anymore%2C%20and%20a%20larger%20chunk%20of%20the%20fees%20paid%20are%20going%20to%20GP's%20business%20instead%20of%20its%20moneymakers.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BHow%20rich%20do%20you%20need%20your%20hedge%20fund%20manager%20to%20be%3F%26quot%3B%20he%20asked.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EBecause%20he%20and%20others%20in%20the%20industry%20are%20happy%20to%20pay%20when%20performance%20comes%20along%20with%20it.%20He%20said%20some%20of%20his%20portfolio's%20best%20performers%20are%20firms%20that%20charge%20higher%20fees%2C%20and%20there%20are%20plenty%20of%20examples%20in%20the%20industry%20of%20leading%20managers%20charging%20exorbitant%20fees%20because%20investors%20know%20it%20is%20worth%20it.%20For%20instance%2C%20the%20holy%20grail%20of%20hedge%20funds%2C%20Renaissance%20Technologies'%20famed%20Medallion%20fund%2C%20charges%20its%20investors%20more%20than%20double%20the%20once-standard%202-and-20%20%E2%80%94%20and%20would%20have%20allocators%20knocking%20down%20their%20door%20if%20they%20opened%20to%20new%20capital.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EBergstrom%20is%20also%20happy%20to%20support%20firms%20when%20it%20makes%20sense.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EFor%20example%2C%20he%20said%2C%20a%20small%20firm%20they're%20invested%20in%20asked%20for%20a%20fee%20increase%20because%20their%20talent%20was%20at%20risk%20of%20being%20poached%20by%20some%20of%20the%20pod%20shops.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThey%20told%20us%20that%20this%20was%20to%20pay%20their%20people%2C%20not%20themselves%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BWe%20thought%20that%20was%20very%20reasonable%20and%20went%20ahead%20with%20it.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cdiv%3ERead%20the%20original%20article%20on%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fhedge-fund-investors-push-back-on-talent-fees-2024-8%5C%22%3EBusiness%20Insider%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1724058002000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F66b16a73393cd3c8629b7540%3Fformat%3Djpeg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fhedge-fund-investors-push-back-on-talent-fees-2024-8%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22This%20year%20was%20the%20first%20time%20hedge%20fund%20fees%20rose%20in%20a%20decade.%20Allocators%20are%20not%20pleased.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22bsaacks%40businessinsider.com%20(Bradley%20Saacks)%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A29%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fhedge-fund-investors-push-back-on-talent-fees-2024-8%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22I%20studied%20in%20North%20Korea%20for%20a%20month.%20The%20isolation%20shocked%20me%20the%20most.%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%224000%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22A%20man%20in%20his%20early%20twenties%20stands%20next%20to%20several%20flags%20and%20in%20front%20of%20a%20large%20monument%20at%20an%20intersection%20in%20Pyongyang.%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F66b60018955b01c3294d2309%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%223000%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3ETodor%20Merdjanov%20at%20an%20intersection%20in%20Pyongyang.%3Cp%3ECourtesy%20of%20Todor%20Merdjanov%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cul%3E%3Cli%3ETodor%20Merdjanov%20recounts%20his%20month%20studying%20at%20Kim%20Il%20Sung%20University%20in%20North%20Korea.%3C%2Fli%3E%3Cli%3EHe%20attended%20intensive%20language%20classes%20by%2