20description%20from%20Tesla's%20Careers%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.tesla.com%2Fcareers%2Fsearch%2Fjob%2F-data-collection-operator-tesla-bot-night-shift-223213%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Epage%3C%2Fa%3E.%20In%20addition%20to%20collecting%20data%2C%20workers%20are%20also%20expected%20to%20analyze%20the%20information%20they've%20gathered%2C%20write%20daily%20reports%20on%20it%2C%20as%20well%20as%20work%20on%20some%20minor%20tasks%20related%20to%20their%20equipment%20and%20its%20software.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIt%20also%20has%20very%20specific%20height%20requirements%20and%20calls%20for%20people%20between%20five%20foot%2C%20seven%20inches%20and%20five%20foot%2C%20eleven%20inches.%20Christian%20Hubicki%2C%20a%20roboticist%20out%20of%20Florida%20A%26amp%3BM%20University%2C%20said%20Tesla%20is%20likely%20looking%20for%20individuals%20who%20will%20not%20only%20fit%20into%20the%20specific%20suits%2C%20but%20will%20also%20have%20similar%20sizing%20to%20the%20robot%2C%20which%20Musk%20has%20said%20will%20clock%20in%20around%20five%20foot%2C%20eight%20inches.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ETesla%20is%20also%20looking%20for%20someone%20that%20will%20be%20comfortable%20wearing%20the%20motion-capture%20suit%20and%20VR%20headset%20for%20long%20stretches%20of%20time%20and%20will%20be%20able%20to%20withstand%20some%20of%20the%20disorientation%20and%20%26quot%3BVR%20sickness%20symptoms%26quot%3B%20that%20can%20come%20with%20using%20the%20gear%20for%20extended%20periods.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%22854%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Tesla%20has%20several%20requirements%20for%20the%20role.%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F66bf46d61aa2ac29ee31ce6a%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22343%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EA%20screenshot%20of%20Tesla's%20job%20listing%2C%20which%20has%20several%20requirements.%3Cp%3ETesla%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3ETesla%20is%20hiring%20full-time%20workers%20for%20the%20role%20and%20is%20willing%20to%20pay%20between%20%2425.25%20to%20%2448%20per%20hour%2C%20according%20to%20the%20job%20listing.%20The%20role%20is%20available%20with%20multiple%20shifts%2C%20including%20from%208%20a.m.%20to%204%3A30%20p.m.%2C%204%20p.m.%20to%2012%3A30%20a.m.%2C%20and%2012%3A00%20a.m.%20to%208%3A30%20a.m.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAnimesh%20Garg%2C%20a%20senior%20researcher%20at%20Nvidia%20Research%20and%20a%20robotics%20professor%20at%20Georgie%20Institute%20of%20Technology%2C%20said%20the%20job%20likely%20entails%20collecting%20data%20through%20simply%20performing%20tasks%20in%20the%20motion-capture%20suit%20that%20can%20be%20recorded%20and%20later%20analyzed%20by%20data%20annotators%20in%20order%20to%20train%20the%20AI%20system%2C%20as%20well%20as%20tele-operating%20the%20humanoid%20robot%20directly.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ETesla's%20Optimus%20social%20media%20account%20provided%20a%20peek%20into%20what%20the%20job%20entails%20last%20year.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20video%20clip%20shows%20an%20operator%20in%20a%20motion-capture%20suit%2C%20with%20haptic%20gloves%20and%20a%20VR%20headset%20picking%20up%20objects%20while%20a%20virtual%20version%20of%20the%20Tesla%20Optimus%20bot%20performs%20the%20same%20movements.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%22596%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Tesla%20shared%20a%20video%20showing%20how%20it%20uses%20motion%20capture%20suits%20last%20year.%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F66be291db4912df3ae1bfafd%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22469%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3ETesla%20shared%20a%20video%20showing%20how%20it%20uses%20motion-capture%20suits%20last%20year.%3Cp%3EX%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3EEarlier%20this%20year%2C%20Tesla%20appeared%20to%20go%20on%20a%20hiring%20spree%20for%20the%20role.%20More%20than%2050%20different%20people%20have%20worked%20in%20the%20role%20over%20different%20periods%20over%20the%20past%20year%2C%20according%20to%20a%20Business%20Insider%20review%20of%20LinkedIn%20data.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ETesla%20is%20likely%20looking%20to%20gather%20vast%20amounts%20of%20data%2C%20experts%20say.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BIt's%20the%20exact%20same%20thing%20they're%20doing%20with%20Autopilot%2C%26quot%3B%20Jonathan%20Aitken%2C%20a%20robotics%20expert%20out%20of%20the%20University%20of%20Sheffield%2C%20said.%20%26quot%3BBut%20rather%20than%20collecting%20data%20from%20their%20fleet%20of%20cars%2C%20they're%20paying%20people%20to%20come%20into%20the%20factory%20or%20come%20into%20a%20workplace%20and%20undertake%20these%20tasks.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EGarg%2C%20the%20Nvidia%20researcher%20and%20robotics%20professor%2C%20estimates%20that%20Tesla%20should%20be%20aiming%20to%20log%20anywhere%20from%20hundreds%20of%20thousands%20of%20hours%20to%20millions%20of%20hours%20of%20data%20in%20order%20to%20train%20Optimus%20how%20to%20work%20in%20Tesla's%20factories%20%E2%80%94%20a%20feat%20that%20could%20take%20a%20lot%20of%20time%20and%20money.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BIt%20extremely%20difficult%20to%20produce%20robots%20at%20scale%2C%26quot%3B%20Garg%20said%2C%20adding%20that%20Tesla's%20Optimus%20robots%20are%20likely%20custom%20built%20and%20assembled%2C%20as%20well%20as%20constantly%20undergoing%20new%20iterations.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThe%20amount%20of%20data%20collection%20you'd%20need%20would%20easily%20be%20half%20a%20billion%20dollars%20and%20the%20real%20question%20is%20'Even%20if%20you%20do%20that%2C%20do%20you%20succeed%3F'%20Because%20there%20is%20no%20guarantee%20of%20success%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20added.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20use%20of%20motion-capture%20suits%20and%20tele-operation%20in%20robot%20training%20is%20far%20from%20a%20new%20practice%2C%20but%20Tesla%20is%20among%20the%20first%20to%20attempt%20to%20use%20the%20practice%20at%20this%20scale%20and%20to%20perform%20such%20a%20wide%20variety%20of%20generalized%20tasks%2C%20according%20to%20Aitken.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BIn%20the%20manufacturing%20world%2C%20we%20typically%20have%20a%20robot%20that%20can%20do%20one%20task%20really%20really%20well%2C%20but%20it%20doesn't%20usually%20extend%20beyond%20that%2C%26quot%3B%20Aitken%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EA%20spokesperson%20for%20Tesla%20did%20not%20respond%20to%20a%20request%20for%20comment.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3E%3Cem%3EDo%20you%20work%20for%20Tesla%20or%20have%20a%20tip%3F%20Reach%20out%20to%20the%20reporter%20via%20a%20non-work%20email%20and%20device%20at%20gkay%40businessinsider.com%20or%20248-894-6012%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cdiv%3ERead%20the%20original%20article%20on%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Ftesla-job-training-optimus-robot-motion-capture-suit-2024-8%5C%22%3EBusiness%20Insider%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1724057941000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F66be099d955b01c3294eda7c%3Fformat%3Djpeg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Ftesla-job-training-optimus-robot-motion-capture-suit-2024-8%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Willing%20to%20spend%20hours%20in%20a%20motion-capture%20suit%3F%20Tesla%20is%20paying%20between%20%2425%20to%20%2448%20per%20hour%20for%20%26quot%3BData%20Collection%20Operators.%26quot%3B%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22gkay%40businessinsider.com%20(Grace%20Kay)%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A3%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Ftesla-job-training-optimus-robot-motion-capture-suit-2024-8%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22I%20went%20to%20Taco%20Bell%20for%20the%20first%20time.%20I%20thought%20it%20would%20be%20cheaper.%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%222551%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Nora%20in%20Taco%20Bell%20holding%20a%20burrito%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F66b4c51e5da406397bf41e71%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%221913%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EI%20went%20to%20a%20Taco%20Bell%20in%20London%20to%20see%20just%20how%20much%20the%20restaurant%20prioritizes%20value.%20%3Cp%3ENora%20Redmond%2FBusiness%20Insider%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cul%3E%3Cli%3ETaco%20Bell%20reported%20a%205%25%20rise%20in%20same-store%20sales%20in%20the%20most%20recent%20quarter.%3C%2Fli%3E%3Cli%3EThe%20taco%20chain's%20focus%20on%20value%20meals%20has%20attracted%20cost-conscious%20diners%20amid%20rising%20prices.%3C%2Fli%3E%3Cli%3EI%20went%20to%20a%20Taco%20Bell%20in%20London%20to%20see%20how%20cheap%20and%20tasty%20the%20food%20is.%3C%2Fli%3E%3C%2Ful%3E%3Cp%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fhundreds-taco-bell-drive-thrus-ai-operated-by-end-2024-2024-7%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3ETaco%20Bell%3C%2Fa%3E%20has%20been%20doubling%20down%20on%20value%20%E2%80%94%20and%20it's%20working.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAs%20fast%20food%20restaurants%20try%20to%20lure%20cost-conscious%20diners%20back%2C%20the%20taco%20chain%20reported%20a%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Ftaco-bell-cheap-fast-food-gives-diners-what-they-want-2024-8%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3E5%25%20rise%20in%20same-store%20sales%3C%2Fa%3E%20in%20the%20most%20recent%20quarter.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIt%20surpassed%20its%20Yum!%20Brands%20sister%20brands%20%E2%80%94%20KFC%20and%20Pizza%20Hut%20%E2%80%94%20and%20industry%20competitors%20like%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fmcdonalds-expensive-prices-too-high-fast-food-restaurant-falling-sales-2024-7%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EMcDonald's%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20which%20saw%20sales%20fall%20in%20the%20most%20recent%20quarter.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ETaco%20Bell%20has%20homed%20in%20on%20offering%20value%20meals%20while%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Ffast-food-is-expensive-people-annoyed-eating-out-restaurant-2024%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Efast%20food%20prices%20have%20soared%3C%2Fa%3E%20elsewhere%2C%20winning%20over%20customers%20in%20the%20process.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EI%20went%20to%20a%20Taco%20Bell%20restaurant%20in%20Bloomsbury%2C%20central%20London%2C%20for%20the%20first%20time%20to%20see%20just%20how%20cheap%20%E2%80%94%20and%20tasty%20%E2%80%94%20the%20food%20is.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cdiv%3E%3Cdiv%3EThe%20chain%20reopened%20in%20the%20UK%20in%202010%20after%20its%20first%20four%20stores%20all%20closed%20by%20the%20mid-1990s.%20There%20are%20now%20over%20135%20Taco%20Bells%20across%20the%20country.%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%222551%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22The%20store%20front%20of%20Taco%20Bell%20in%20Bloomsbury%2C%20London%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F66b4c5d05da406397bf41ec4%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%221913%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3ETaco%20Bell%20reopened%20in%20the%20UK%20in%202010.%3Cp%3ENora%20Redmond%2FBusiness%20Insider%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3EFast%20food%20chains%20have%20been%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Frestaurants-are-competing-to-offer-the-cheapest-meals-2024-5%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Eramping%20up%20value%20meals%3C%2Fa%3E%20recently%20to%20compete%20for%20customers.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20CEO%20of%20its%20parent%20company%2C%20Yum!%20Brands%2C%20said%20in%20its%20most%20recent%20earnings%20call%20that%20Taco%20Bell's%20sales%20growth%20during%20the%20quarter%20was%20partly%20due%20to%20its%20value%20meals%2C%20which%20keep%20it%20competitive.%20%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3Cdiv%3EIt's%20clear%20from%20the%20moment%20you%20approach%20that%20it's%20trying%20to%20push%20its%20special%20offers.%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%222551%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22The%20inside%20of%20Taco%20Bell%20in%20Bloomsbury%2C%20London%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F66b4c680955b01c3294cd814%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%221913%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EThe%20inside%20of%20the%20restaurant%20could%20have%20benefitted%20form%20more%20space%2C%20but%20it%20is%20in%20central%20London.%3Cp%3ENora%20Redmond%2FBusiness%20Insider%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3EThere%20were%20posters%20on%20the%20storefront%20windows%2C%20and%20promotions%20were%20the%20first%20thing%20you%20saw%20on%20the%20menu.%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3Cdiv%3EYou%20order%20from%20one%20of%20two%20self-service%20screens%2C%20which%20only%20accept%20card%20payments.%20%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%222551%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22One%20of%20the%20screens%20for%20ordering%20food%20in%20Taco%20Bell%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F66b4c6fcb4912df3ae19e73f%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%221913%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EThis%20Taco%20Bell%20had%20two%20self-service%20screens%20to%20speed%20up%20the%20ordering%20process.%20%3Cp%3ENora%20Redmond%2FBusiness%20Insider%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3EThis%20wouldn't%20be%20new%20to%20British%20fast-food%20chains.%20What%20I%20did%20find%20was%20this%20screen%20was%20a%20little%20slow%20to%20react%2C%20and%20the%20other%20one%20was%20actually%20out%20of%20use.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EOverall%2C%20it%20was%20a%20pretty%20seamless%20system%20of%20ordering%20and%20waiting%20for%20your%20number%20to%20be%20called%20before%20collecting%20your%20tray%20from%20a%20staff%20member.%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3Cdiv%3EI%20ordered%20a%20Veggie%20Deluxe%20Box%20along%20with%20a%20cheesy%20roll-up%20from%20its%20Cravings%20Value%20Menu.%20%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%222551%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22The%20Veggie%20Deluxe%20Box%20with%20a%20Pepsi%20Max%2C%20a%20cheese%20roll-up%20and%20a%20burrito%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F66b4ca5fb4912df3ae19e8e5%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%221913%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EThe%20Veggie%20Deluxe%20Box%2C%20a%20cheesy%20roll-up%20and%20a%20double%20cheesy%20black%20bean%20burrito%20cost%20%C2%A312.97%20(%2416.50).%3Cp%3ENora%20Redmond%2FBusiness%20Insider%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3ETaco%20Bell%20overhauled%20its%20%3Ca%