nd%20a%20soda%2C%20costs%20%C2%A33.99%20(%245)%20in%20a%20nearby%20location.%20But%20this%20meal%20doesn't%20include%20a%20dessert%20or%20an%20extra%20side.%20%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3Cdiv%3EI%20had%20high%20hopes%20for%20the%20double%20cheesy%20black%20bean%20burrito%2C%20which%20is%20usually%20what%20I'd%20order%20in%20similar%20restaurants.%20%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%222551%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22The%20Cheesy%20Black%20Bean%20Cravings%20Burrito%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F66b4c868b4912df3ae19e7fb%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%221913%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EThe%20double%20cheesy%20black%20bean%20burrito%20did%20not%20have%20enough%20cheese%2C%20in%20my%20opinion.%20%3Cp%3ENora%20Redmond%2FBusiness%20Insider%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3EThis%20didn't%20really%20meet%20my%20expectations.%20I%20found%20it%20too%20sweet%20and%20felt%20it%20could%20benefit%20from%20more%20cheese.%20The%20burrito%20was%20helped%20by%20the%20seasoned%20fries%2C%20which%20created%20a%20nice%20balance%20between%20the%20salty%20and%20the%20slight%20sugary%20aftertaste.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThere%20is%20absolutely%20nothing%20I%20would%20change%20about%20those%20fries%2C%20I%20didn't%20even%20need%20to%20dip%20them%20in%20anything.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EOn%20its%20own%20from%20the%3Cstrong%3E%20%3C%2Fstrong%3ECravings%20menu%2C%20this%20item%20costs%20%C2%A31.99%20(%242.55).%20It's%20not%20substantial%20enough%20to%20be%20a%20main%20meal%20but%20if%20you're%20just%20looking%20for%20a%20snack%2C%20this%20is%20a%20good%20bet.%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3Cdiv%3EThe%207-layer%20burrito%20was%20the%20most%20filling%20part%20of%20the%20deluxe%20box.%20I%20enjoyed%20the%20combination%20of%20textures.%20%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%221579%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Taco%20Bell's%20veggie%207%20Layer%20Burrito%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F66bdc838955b01c3294ecfa9%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%221184%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3E%3Cp%3ENora%20Redmond%2FBusiness%20Insider%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3EI%20ate%20the%20veggie%207-layer%20burrito.%20Its%20fillings%20were%20black%20beans%2C%20lettuce%2C%20tomatoes%2C%20seasoned%20rice%2C%20a%203-cheese%20blend%2C%20guacamole%20and%20sour%20cream.%20Between%20the%20softness%20of%20the%20wrap%2C%20the%20crunchiness%20of%20the%20lettuce%2C%20and%20the%20chewiness%20of%20the%20black%20beans%2C%20this%20burrito%20had%20a%20fun%20texture.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EI%20thought%20it%20was%20a%20generous%20size%20and%20one%20would%20be%20enough%20for%20lunch.%20This%20was%20probably%20one%20of%20the%20best%20value%20for%20money%20dishes%20on%20the%20menu.%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3Cdiv%3EI%20was%20delighted%20to%20see%20that%20this%20box%20included%20churros.%20They%20smelled%20delicious.%20%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%222551%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22A%20churro%20being%20dunked%20into%20caramel%20sauce%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F66b4c9ba955b01c3294cd9a3%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%221913%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EThe%20churros%20weren't%20oily%20or%20greasy%2C%20and%20they%20didn't%20need%20the%20caramel%20dip.%20%3Cp%3ENora%20Redmond%2FBusiness%20Insider%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3EI%20was%20excited%20to%20bite%20into%20one%20of%20these%20as%20soon%20as%20I%20collected%20my%20tray.%20I%20was%20worried%20they%20might%20be%20greasy%20or%20oily%2C%20but%20was%20pleasantly%20proved%20wrong.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EFor%20me%2C%20the%20churros%20didn't%20actually%20need%20a%20sauce%2C%20and%20the%20caramel%20dip%20they%20did%20come%20with%20was%20too%20sweet%20for%20me.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ETo%20buy%20alone%2C%20these%20cost%20%C2%A32.69%20(%243.45).%20There%20were%20only%20two%20in%20a%20bag%20so%20I%20felt%20this%20price%20was%20a%20bit%20high.%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3Cdiv%3EThe%20cheesy%20roll-up%20was%20fairly%20bland%2C%20but%20it%20did%20cost%20less%2