imgsize-963161.cms%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Ftimesofindia.indiatimes.com%2Fworld%2Feurope%2F7-people-missing-after-tourist-sailboat-sinks-in-storm-off-sicily%2Farticleshow%2F112625153.cms%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22%3Cimg%20border%3D%5C%220%5C%22%20align%3D%5C%22left%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Ftimesofindia.indiatimes.com%2Fphoto%2F112625153.cms%5C%22%20hspace%3D%5C%2210%5C%22%3E%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Ftimesofindia.indiatimes.com%2Fworld%2Feurope%2F7-people-missing-after-tourist-sailboat-sinks-in-storm-off-sicily%2Farticleshow%2F112625153.cms%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Ftimesofindia-indiatimes-com.cdn.ampproject.org%2Fc%2Fs%2Ftimesofindia.indiatimes.com%2Fworld%2Feurope%2F7-people-missing-after-tourist-sailboat-sinks-in-storm-off-sicily%2Famp_articleshow%2F112625153.cms%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Ftimesofindia.indiatimes.com%2Fworld%2Feurope%2F7-people-missing-after-tourist-sailboat-sinks-in-storm-off-sicily%2Famp_articleshow%2F112625153.cms%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22What%20Is%20Lateral%20Entry%20In%20Bureaucracy%20That%20Triggered%20BJP%20vs%20Congress%20Debate%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cp%3EThe%20Union%20Public%20Service%20Commission%20(UPSC)%20has%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fupsc.gov.in%2Frecruitment%2Frecruitment-advertisements%5C%22%3Eissued%20an%20advertisement%3C%2Fa%3E%20seeking%20%26quot%3Btalented%20and%20motivated%20Indian%20nationals%26quot%3B%20for%20lateral%20recruitment%20to%20various%20senior%20positions%20within%20the%20Union%20government.%20These%20positions%20include%20Joint%20Secretary%2C%20Director%2C%20and%20Deputy%20Secretary%20in%2024%20ministries%2C%20with%20a%20total%20of%2045%20posts%20up%20for%20grabs.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThis%20move%20has%20triggered%20a%20debate%20on%20lateral%20entry%20into%20bureaucracy%2C%20especially%20after%20Congress%20leader%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Flateral-entry-upsc-rss-rahul-gandhi-akhilesh-yadav-in-lateral-entry-row-rahul-gandhi-renews-attack-on-dalits-criticism-6369000%5C%22%3ERahul%20Gandhi's%20recent%20criticism%3C%2Fa%3E%20of%20the%20process%2C%20which%20the%20BJP%20has%20countered%20by%20pointing%20out%20that%20the%20concept%20was%20initially%20developed%20under%20a%20Congress-led%20government.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch3%3E%3Cstrong%3EWhat%20Is%20Lateral%20Entry%3F%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh3%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ELateral%20entry%20into%20bureaucracy%20refers%20to%20the%20recruitment%20of%20individuals%20from%20outside%20the%20traditional%20government%20service%20cadres%2C%20such%20as%20the%20Indian%20Administrative%20Service%20(IAS)%2C%20to%20fill%20mid%20and%20senior-level%20positions%20in%20government%20departments.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20lateral%20entry%20process%20was%20formally%20introduced%20during%20Prime%20Minister%20Narendra%20Modi's%20tenure%2C%20with%20the%20first%20set%20of%20vacancies%20announced%20in%202018.%20This%20marked%20a%20departure%20from%20the%20traditional%20system%20where%20senior%20bureaucratic%20positions%20were%20almost%20exclusively%20filled%20by%20career%20civil%20servants.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ELateral%20entrants%20are%20typically%20hired%20on%20contracts%20ranging%20from%20three%20to%20five%20years%2C%20with%20the%20potential%20for%20extensions%20based%20on%20performance%20and%20the%20needs%20of%20the%20government.%20These%20individuals%20are%20expected%20to%20bring%20expertise%20that%20can%20help%20address%20complex%20challenges%20in%20governance%20and%20policy%20implementation.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20current%20advertisement%20by%20the%20UPSC%20includes%20positions%20at%20three%20levels%3A%20Joint%20Secretary%2C%20Director%2C%20and%20Deputy%20Secretary.%20They%20often%20serve%20as%20the%20administrative%20heads%20of%20specific%20wings%20within%20departments%20and%20are%20key%20decision-makers.%20The%20government's%20rationale%20behind%20lateral%20entry%20is%20twofold%3A%20to%20bring%20in%20fresh%20talent%20and%20to%20augment%20the%20availability%20of%20skilled%20manpower%20in%20the%20administration.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20concept%20of%20lateral%20entry%20into%20bureaucracy%20is%20not%20new.%20According%20to%20government%20sources%2C%20the%20idea%20was%20first%20proposed%20during%20the%20United%20Progressive%20Alliance%20(UPA)%20government%2C%20led%20by%20Congress%2C%20in%20the%20mid-2000s.%20In%202005%2C%20the%20UPA%20established%20the%20Second%20Administrative%20Reforms%20Commission%20(ARC)%20under%20the%20chairmanship%20of%20Veerappa%20Moily.%20The%20Commission%20was%20tasked%20with%20recommending%20reforms%20the%20Indian%20administrative%20system.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20its%2010th%20report%20titled%20'Refurbishing%20of%20Personnel%20Administration%20-%20Scaling%20New%20Heights'%2C%20the%20second%20ARC%20made%20a%20strong%20case%20for%20lateral%20entry.%20It%20argued%20that%20certain%20government%20roles%20require%20specialised%20knowledge%20and%20expertise%20that%20may%20not%20be%20readily%20available%20within%20the%20traditional%20civil%20services.%20To%20fill%20these%20gaps%2C%20the%20ARC%20recommended%20recruiting%20professionals%20from%20the%20private%20sector%2C%20academia%2C%20and%20PSUs%2C%20reports%20news%20agency%20IANS.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch3%3E%3Cstrong%3ERahul%20Gandhi's%20Criticism%20And%20BJP's%20Response%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh3%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ERahul%20Gandhi%20has%20been%20vocal%20in%20his%20opposition%20to%20lateral%20entry%2C%20accusing%20the%20Modi%20government%20of%20using%20it%20as%20a%20backdoor%20to%20recruit%20officers%20loyal%20to%20the%20BJP's%20ideological%20mentor%2C%20the%20Rashtriya%20Swayamsevak%20Sangh%20(RSS).%20In%20a%20recent%20post%20on%20X%20(formerly%20Twitter)%2C%20Mr%20Gandhi%20alleged%20that%20lateral%20entry%20is%20being%20used%20to%20sidestep%20the%20UPSC%20and%20deny%20reservations%20to%20candidates%20from%20Scheduled%20Castes%20(SC)%2C%20Scheduled%20Tribes%20(ST)%2C%20and%20Other%20Backward%20Classes%20(OBC).%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cblockquote%20class%3D%5C%22twitter-tweet%5C%22%3E%5Cn%3Cp%20dir%3D%5C%22ltr%5C%22%20lang%3D%5C%22en%5C%22%3ELateral%20entry%20is%20an%20attack%20on%20Dalits%2C%20OBCs%20and%20Adivasis.%3Cbr%3E%5Cn%3Cbr%3E%5CnBJP's%20distorted%20version%20of%20Ram%20Rajya%20seeks%20to%20destroy%20the%20Constitution%20and%20snatch%20reservations%20from%20Bahujans.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%E2%80%94%20Rahul%20Gandhi%20(%40RahulGandhi)%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Ftwitter.com%2FRahulGandhi%2Fstatus%2F1825407202644897798%3Fref_src%3Dtwsrc%255Etfw%5C%22%3EAugust%2019%2C%202024%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fblockquote%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ECongress%20President%20Mallikarjun%20Kharge%20described%20lateral%20entry%20as%20part%20of%20a%20%26quot%3Bwell-planned%20conspiracy%26quot%3B%20to%20exclude%20marginalised%20communities%20from%20government%20jobs.%20Other%20opposition%20leaders%2C%20such%20as%20Rashtriya%20Janata%20Dal's%20Tejashwi%20Yadav%20and%20former%20Uttar%20Pradesh%20Chief%20Minister%20Mayawati%2C%20have%20also%20condemned%20the%20move%2C%20arguing%20that%20it%20deprives%20underprivileged%20candidates%20of%20opportunities%20for%20advancement%20within%20the%20government.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHowever%2C%20the%20BJP%20has%20hit%20back%2C%20pointing%20out%20that%20the%20concept%20of%20lateral%20entry%20was%20developed%20during%20the%20Congress-led%20United%20Progressive%20Alliance%20(UPA)%20government.%20Union%20Minister%20Ashwini%20Vaishnaw%20claimed%20that%20the%20Second%20Administrative%20Reforms%20Commission%20(ARC)%2C%20chaired%20by%20Congress%20leader%20Veerappa%20Moily%2C%20recommended%20lateral%20recruitment%20to%20fill%20gaps%20in%20roles%20requiring%20specialised%20knowledge.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cblockquote%20class%3D%5C%22twitter-tweet%5C%22%3E%5Cn%3Cp%20dir%3D%5C%22ltr%5C%22%20lang%3D%5C%22en%5C%22%3ELateral%20entry%3Cbr%3E%5Cn%3Cbr%3E%5CnINC%20hypocrisy%20is%20evident%20on%20lateral%20entry%20matter.%20It%20was%20the%20UPA%20government%20which%20developed%20the%20concept%20of%20lateral%20entry.%3Cbr%3E%5Cn%3Cbr%3E%5CnThe%20second%20Admin%20Reforms%20Commission%20(ARC)%20was%20established%20in%202005%20under%20UPA%20government.%20Shri%20Veerappa%20Moily%20chaired%20it.%3Cbr%3E%5Cn%3Cbr%3E%5CnUPA%20period%20ARC%E2%80%A6%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%E2%80%94%20Ashwini%20Vaishnaw%20(%40AshwiniVaishnaw)%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Ftwitter.com%2FAshwiniVaishnaw%2Fstatus%2F1825221158721257860%3Fref_src%3Dtwsrc%255Etfw%5C%22%3EAugust%2018%2C%202024%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fblockquote%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMr%20Vaishnaw%20also%20defended%20the%20current%20government's%20implementation%20of%20lateral%20entry%20by%20saying%20that%20the%20recruitment%20process%20is%20transparent%20and%20conducted%20through%20the%20UPSC.%20He%20argued%20that%20this%20reform%20would%20improve%20governance%20by%20bringing%20in%20professionals%20with%20the%20necessary%20expertise.%3Cbr%3E%5Cn%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1724056980000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2024-08%2Foipmuqj8_rahul-gandhi-ashwini-vaishnaw_625x300_19_August_24.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fwhat-is-lateral-entry-in-bureaucracy-that-triggered-bjp-vs-congress-debate-6369676%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Lateral%20entry%20into%20bureaucracy%20refers%20to%20the%20recruitment%20of%20individuals%20from%20outside%20the%20traditional%20government%20service%20cadres%2C%20such%20as%20the%20Indian%20Administrative%20Service%20(IAS)%2C%20to%20fill%20mid%20and%20senior-level%20positions%20in%20government%20departments.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fwhat-is-lateral-entry-in-bureaucracy-that-triggered-bjp-vs-congress-debate-6369676%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Ahead%20of%20The%20Great%20Indian%20Kapil%20Show's%20second%20season%2C%20Kapil%20Sharma%20and%20Sunil%20Grover%20went%20for%20a%20spiritual%20retreat%20together%3B%20latter%20asks%20'