ctor-didnt-hear-patients-painful-cries-during-colonoscopy-due-to-missing-hearing-aids%2Farticleshow%2F112623545.cms%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Ftimesofindia-indiatimes-com.cdn.ampproject.org%2Fc%2Fs%2Ftimesofindia.indiatimes.com%2Fworld%2Fus%2Findian-american-doctor-didnt-hear-patients-painful-cries-during-colonoscopy-due-to-missing-hearing-aids%2Famp_articleshow%2F112623545.cms%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Ftimesofindia.indiatimes.com%2Fworld%2Fus%2Findian-american-doctor-didnt-hear-patients-painful-cries-during-colonoscopy-due-to-missing-hearing-aids%2Famp_articleshow%2F112623545.cms%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Vinesh%20Reveals%20Gift%20From%20Brother%20On%20Raksha%20Bandhan%3A%20%26quot%3BWhole%20Life's%20Earning%26quot%3B%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cp%3EVinesh%20Phogat%2C%20since%20her%20return%20to%20India%20from%20Paris%20Olympics%202024%2C%20has%20been%20showered%20with%20love%20from%20all%20quarters.%20After%20an%20Olympic%20heart-break%20for%20getting%20disqualified%20from%20the%20women's%2050kg%20wrestling%20final%2C%20Vinesh%20returned%20to%20India%20on%20Saturday.%20She%20received%20a%20rousing%20welcome%20at%20the%20New%20Delhi%20airport.%20Thousands%20felicitated%20her%20on%20the%20way%20to%20Babali%2C%20where%20Vinesh'%20family%20resides.%20On%20MOnday%2C%20Vinesh%20Phogat%20celebrated%20Raksha%20Bandhan.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EA%20special%20post%20has%20gone%20viral%20on%20social%20media%20where%20Vinesh%20can%20be%20seen%20holding%20a%20bundle%20of%20Rs%20500%20notes.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BI%20am%20almost%2030%20years%20old.%20Last%20year%20he%20gave%20me%20Rs%20500.%20After%20that%20this%20(points%20to%20a%20bundle%20of%20currency%20note).%20He%20has%20earned%20this%20much%20money%20only%20in%20his%20whole%20life%20(jokingly)%2C%20which%20he%20has%20given%20to%20me%2C%26quot%3B%20Vinesh%20said.%20His%20brother%20also%20started%20started%20smiling%20after%20her%20statement.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cblockquote%20class%3D%5C%22twitter-tweet%5C%22%3E%5Cn%3Cp%20dir%3D%5C%22ltr%5C%22%20lang%3D%5C%22en%5C%22%3ECharkhi%20Dadri%2C%20Haryana%3A%20Wrestler%20Vinesh%20Phogat%20celebrates%20Raksha%20Bandhan%20with%20her%20brother%20in%20their%20village%20Balali%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Ft.co%2FYgahqHmDPq%5C%22%3Epic.twitter.com%2FYgahqHmDPq%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%E2%80%94%20IANS%20(%40ians_india)%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Ftwitter.com%2Fians_india%2Fstatus%2F1825438914150043781%3Fref_src%3Dtwsrc%255Etfw%5C%22%3EAugust%2019%2C%202024%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fblockquote%3E%5Cn%5Cn%3Cp%3EOn%20her%20way%20to%20Balali%20from%20Delhi%2C%20Vinesh%20was%20felicitated%20by%20her%20supporters%20and%20'khap'%20panchayats%20in%20several%20villages%2C%20with%20the%20135km-long%20journey%20taking%20her%20almost%2013%20hours%20on%20Saturday.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThis%20was%20after%20hundreds%20of%20supporters%20gathered%20outside%20the%20IGI%20airport%20to%20give%20a%20rousing%20welcome%20to%20Vinesh%2C%20who%20was%20disqualified%20for%20being%20overweight%20after%20reaching%20the%2050kg%20final%20at%20the%20Olympics.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHer%20disqualification%20had%20created%20a%20furore%20in%20India%20and%20the%20wrestling%20world.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EVinesh's%20appeal%20against%20her%20disqualification%20was%20rejected%20by%20the%20Court%20of%20Arbitration%20for%20Sport%20(CAS).%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EVinesh%2C%2029%2C%20reached%20her%20native%20village%20around%20midnight%20and%20was%20accorded%20a%20grand%20welcome.%20Her%20neighbours%20and%20friends%20met%20her%20with%20tears%20and%20smiles%20and%20patted%20her%20for%20the%20courage%20she%20has%20shown.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EExhausted%20after%20a%20tiring%20journey%20that%20began%20in%20Paris%2C%20Vinesh%20addressed%20the%20gathering%20before%20calling%20it%20a%20day.%20The%20two-time%20World%20Championships%20medallist%20wished%20that%20someone%20from%20Balali%20would%20better%20her%20wrestling%20achievements.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BIt%20would%20be%20disappointing%20if%20no%20wrestler%20emerged%20from%20this%20village.%20We%20have%20paved%20the%20way%2C%20given%20hope%20with%20our%20achievements.%20I%20request%20you%20all%20to%20support%20the%20women%20in%20this%20village.%20They%20need%20your%20support%2C%20hope%20and%20trust%20if%20they%20have%20to%20replace%20us%20in%20future%2C%26quot%3B%20Vinesh%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThey%20can%20achieve%20a%20lot.%20All%20they%20need%20is%20your%20support.%20I%20will%20always%20be%20indebted%20to%20this%20nation%2C%20this%20village%20for%20giving%20me%20so%20much%20love%20and%20respect.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BWhatever%20I%20have%20learnt%20in%20wrestling%2C%20I%20don't%20know%20if%20that%20is%20god-gifted%20or%20my%20hard%20work%20but%20whatever%20I%20have%20I%20would%20like%20to%20share%20with%20my%20sisters%20from%20this%20village%20and%20I%20wish%20they%20achieve%20greater%20heights%20than%20me.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BI%20can%20then%20say%20with%20pride%20that%20she%20is%20from%20my%20village%20and%20I%20have%20trained%20her.%20I%20want%20that%20(my)%20records%20are%20broken%20by%20wrestlers%20from%20this%20village.%20Thank%20you%20all%20for%20staying%20up%20so%20late%20in%20the%20night%20for%20me.%26quot%3B%20Vinesh%20is%20a%20two-time%20CWG%20gold%20medallist%2C%20Asian%20Games%20champion%20and%20has%20won%20eight%20Asian%20Championships%20medals.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EBefore%20arriving%20in%20Balali%2C%20Vinesh%20had%20said%20that%20her%20fight%20against%20the%20Wrestling%20Federation%20of%20India%20(WFI)%20would%20continue.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BI%20want%20to%20thank%20all%20the%20people%20who%20supported%20us%20in%20our%20struggle.%20Life%20itself%20is%20a%20struggle.%20Our%20fight%20has%20not%20ended%20and%20it%20will%20continue%2C%26quot%3B%20said%20Vinesh.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ELater%20addressing%20press%20in%20Balali%2C%20she%20reiterated%20the%20resolve.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThis%20Olympic%20medal%20is%2