Congo%2C%20where%20the%20disease%20has%20been%20spreading%20since%20last%20year.%20The%20country%20saw%20more%20than%2096%25%20of%20the%20world's%20roughly%2017%2C000%20recorded%20cases%20of%20Mpox%20this%20year.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThough%20India%20has%20not%20reported%20any%20cases%20yet%2C%20the%20Central%20government%20is%20keeping%20a%20close%20eye%20on%20the%20situation.%20Our%20healthcare%20infrastructure%20faced%20severe%20challenges%20during%20the%20Covid-19%20pandemic%2C%20which%20resulted%20in%20thousands%20of%20deaths.%20One%20wouldn't%20wish%20to%20be%20caught%20unawares%20this%20time.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch2%3E%3Cstrong%3EIs%20Mpox%20As%20Dangerous%20As%20Covid-19%20Or%20Swine%20Flu%3F%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh2%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMpox%20is%20a%20zoonotic%20infection%20that%20causes%20flu-like%20symptoms%20and%20skin%20lesions.%20Fatal%20in%20some%20cases%2C%20the%20WHO%20first%20declared%20it%20a%20global%20emergency%20in%202022.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMpox%20virus%20can%20be%20categorised%20into%20two%20clades%3A%20Clade%201%20and%20Clade%202.%20The%20first%2C%20which%20is%20found%20mainly%20in%20Central%20African%20countries%2C%20is%20more%20severe%20and%20has%20a%20high%20mortality%20rate.%20Clade%202%20has%20milder%20symptoms%20and%20is%20found%20in%20western%20Africa.%20The%20latter%20caused%20a%20public%20health%20emergency%20in%202022%2C%20wherein%20some%20300%20cases%20%E2%80%94%20though%20mild%20%E2%80%94%20were%20reported%20from%20Sweden.%20This%20time%2C%20it's%20the%20newer%20and%20more%20serious%20Clade%201b%2C%20identified%20in%20September%20last%20year%2C%20that%20has%20been%20driving%20the%20current%20outbreak.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThough%20experts%20worry%20that%20Mpox%20may%20be%20as%20dangerous%20as%20Covid-19%20or%20the%20swine%20flu%2C%20there%20is%20a%20difference%20in%20the%20nature%20of%20transmission.%20Both%20Covid-19%20and%20swine%20flu%20were%20highly%20infectious%20because%20they%20were%20airborne.%20In%20contrast%2C%20Mpox%20is%20transmitted%20through%20close%20skin-to-skin%20contact%2C%20talking%20or%20breathing%20close%20to%20an%20infected%20person%2C%20or%20using%20their%20soiled%20clothes%20or%20bedsheets.%20%E2%80%9CMpox%20is%20unlikely%20to%20become%20a%20pandemic%20like%20Covid-19%20primarily%20due%20to%20its%20mode%20of%20spread.%20It%20requires%20very%20close%20and%20physical%20contact%2C%20unlike%20the%20airborne%20SARS-CoV-2.%20Also%2C%20symptoms%20like%20blisters%20on%20the%20skin%20are%20more%20visible%20indicators%20and%20therefore%2C%20it's%20easier%20to%20identify%20the%20disease%20and%20isolate%20a%20person%20to%20contain%20the%20spread%2C%E2%80%9D%20says%20Rakesh%20K.%20Mishra%2C%20former%20director%20of%20the%20Centre%20for%20Cellular%20and%20Molecular%20Biology.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIndia's%20first%20Mpox%20case%20was%20recorded%20in%20Kerala%20in%202022%2C%20from%20a%20traveller%20from%20the%20UAE.%20Soon%2C%20the%20virus%20spread%20within%20the%20country%2C%20with%20cases%20emerging%20in%20Delhi%20even%20from%20individuals%20who%20had%20no%20recent%20international%20travel.%20India%20reported%2027%20confirmed%20cases%20and%20one%20death%20that%20year%2C%20according%20to%20WHO.%20The%20last%20case%20in%20the%20country%20was%20in%20March%20this%20year%2C%20in%20Kerala%2C%20and%20since%20then%2C%20no%20new%20cases%20have%20been%20recorded.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch2%3E%3Cstrong%3EHow%20To%20Stay%20Safe%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh2%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20response%20to%20the%20WHO's%20warning%2C%20both%20Central%20and%20state%20governments%20have%20sprung%20into%20action.%20There%20are%20monkeypox%20advisories%20in%20place%20and%20public%20health%20measures%20are%20being%20taken.%20Both%20the%20Indian%20Council%20of%20Medical%20Research%20(ICMR)%20and%20the%20National%20Centre%20for%20Disease%20Control%20(NCDC)%20are%20closely%20monitoring%20the%20situation%20and%20reviewing%20international%20trends.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20Tamil%20Nadu%2C%20the%20Directorate%20of%20Public%20Health%20and%20Preventive%20Medicine%20(DPH)%20has%20already%20issued%20alerts.%20Reports%20say%20that%20passengers%20arriving%20from%20the%20Democratic%20Republic%20of%20Congo%20and%20Central%20African%20countries%20are%20being%20tracked%20by%20airport%20health%20officers%20and%20port%20health%20personnel.%20Both%20Hyderabad%20and%20New%20Delhi%20%E2%80%94%20cities%20popular%20among%20African%20students%20pursuing%20higher%20education%20%E2%80%94%20have%20also%20been%20placed%20on%20high%20alert.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch2%3E%3Cstrong%3EThe%20Need%20For%20Vaccines%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh2%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20first%20Mpox%20strain%20was%20isolated%20by%20ICMR%20researchers%20in%202022.%20Pharmaceutical%20companies%20and%20drug%20manufacturers%20are%20being%20called%20upon%20to%20develop%20vaccines%20and%20testing%20kits%20for%20the%20virus.%20Existing%20vaccines%20for%20smallpox%20and%20chickenpox%20might%20also%20offer%20protection%20in%20India.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAbout%20other%20prevention%20strategies%2C%20Mishra%20says%2C%20%E2%80%9CIt%20is%20important%20to%20closely%20monitor%20the%20spread%20of%20the%20disease%20in%20different%20countries%20and%20be%20ready%20for%20screening%20by%20already%20available%20methods%20of%20DNA-based%20diagnostics.%20There%20is%20an%20effective%20vaccine%20already%20available%20but%20supply%20of%20that%20may%20not%20be%20easy%20to%20ensure.%E2%80%9D%C2%A0%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CSimple%20practices%20like%20avoiding%20close%20physical%20contact%20with%20suspected%2Fpotentially%20infected%20person%2C%20maintaining%20distance%20from%20people%20with%20symptoms%2C%20and%20wearing%20a%20mask%2C%20should%20be%20effective%20in%20containing%20the%20spread%20of%20the%20infection%2C%E2%80%9D%20Mishra%20adds.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EDeveloped%20nations%2C%20mostly%20those%20in%20Europe%2C%20already%20have%20vaccines%20available%20for%20those%20at%20greater%20risk%20of%20monkeypox.%20And%20given%20the%20high%20quality%20of%20healthcare%20there%2C%20containing%20the%20disease%20will%20be%20less%20challenging.%20It's%20underdeveloped%20African%20countries%2C%20which%20have%20neither%20vaccines%20nor%20the%20resources%20to%20buy%20them%2C%20that%20remain%20at%20most%20risk%20and%20which%20need%20the%20most%20help.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cem%3E(Bharti%20Mishra%20Nath%20is%20Contributing%20Editor%2C%20NDTV)%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EDisclaimer%3A%20These%20are%20the%20personal%20opinions%20of%20the%20author%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1724052960000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2024-08%2F1agedtko_monkeypox_625x300_19_August_24.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Fopinion%2Fis-india-really-at-risk-of-an-mpox-outbreak-6369408%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22The%20WHO%2C%20on%20August%2014%2C%20declared%20the%20current%20upsurge%20of%20Mpox%20or%20Monkeypox%20in%20Central%20Africa%20as%20a%20global%20emergency%20requiring%20urgent%20action.%20Though%20India%20has%20not%20reported%20any%20cases%20yet%2C%20the%20Central%20government%20is%20keeping%20a%20close%20eye%20on%20the%20situation.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Fopinion%2Fis-india-really-at-risk-of-an-mpox-outbreak-6369408%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Ola%20Electric%20share%20price%20rise%3A%20Madness%20beyond%20fundamentals%2C%20say%20analysts%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%22%2C%22published%22%3A1724052887000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fbsmedia.business-standard.com%2F_media%2Fbs%2Fimg%2Farticle%2F2023-12%2F24%2Fthumb%2Ffeaturecrop%2F400X400%2F1703437504-904.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.business-standard.com%2Fmarkets%2Fnews%2Fola-electric-share-price-rise-madness-beyond-fundamentals-say-analysts-124081900344_1.html%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Ola%20Electric%20share%20price%20target%3A%20Since%20its%20listing%20on%20August%209%2C%20Ola%20Electric%20stock%20has%