show%2F112621552.cms%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Mohun%20Bagan%20Captain%20Leads%20Protest%20March%20Against%20Kolkata%20Rape%20Horror%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cp%3EKeeping%20their%20bitter%20rivalry%20aside%2C%20and%20braving%20relentless%20downpour%2C%20thousand%20of%20fans%20of%20Kolkata's%20'Big%20Three'%20football%20clubs%20--%20Mohun%20Bagan%2C%20East%20Bengal%20and%20Mohammedan%20Sporting%20--%20came%20together%20to%20protest%20against%20the%20alleged%20rape%20and%20murder%20of%20a%20doctor%20at%20RG%20Kar%20Medical%20College%20and%20Hospital%2C%20Kolkata%20on%20Sunday.%20Unprecedented%20scenes%20were%20witnessed%20outside%20the%20Salt%20Lake%20Stadium%20as%20India%20defender%20and%20Mohun%20Bagan%20captain%20Subhasish%20Bose%2C%20accompanied%20by%20his%20wife%20Kasturi%20Chetri%2C%20and%20All%20India%20Football%20Federation%20president%20Kalyan%20Chaubey%20joined%20the%20protest%20march%2C%20%26quot%3Bdemanding%20justice%26quot%3B%20for%20the%20RG%20Kar%20victim.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cblockquote%20data-media-max-width%3D%5C%22560%5C%22%20class%3D%5C%22twitter-tweet%5C%22%3E%5Cn%3Cp%20dir%3D%5C%22ltr%5C%22%20lang%3D%5C%22en%5C%22%3EThe%20RG%20Kar%20incident%20was%20absolutely%20horrific%20and%20mind%20numbing%2C%20but%20the%20details%20coming%20out%20along%20with%20the%20authorities'%20attempts%20to%20hide%20the%20truth%20and%20silence%20the%20people%20is%20beyond%20shocking.%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Ft.co%2FRxMH0r6le3%5C%22%3Epic.twitter.com%2FRxMH0r6le3%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%E2%80%94%20Subhasish%20Bose%20(%40subhasis_bose15)%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Ftwitter.com%2Fsubhasis_bose15%2Fstatus%2F1825219216091549812%3Fref_src%3Dtwsrc%255Etfw%5C%22%3EAugust%2018%2C%202024%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fblockquote%3E%5Cn%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BI've%20come%20here%20as%20a%20commoner.%20Justice%20is%20needed%20to%20ensure%20that%20this%20incident%20is%20never%20repeated.%20The%20culprits%20should%20receive%20proper%20punishment.%20We%20will%20continue%20our%20protests%20until%20justice%20is%20served%2C%26quot%3B%20said%20Bose%20while%20his%20wife%20was%20seen%20showing%20a%20placard%20with%20'We%20want%20justice.%20Justice%20for%20RG%20Kar'.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BFor%20the%20first%20time%2C%20fans%20of%20Mohun%20Bagan%2C%20East%20Bengal%2C%20and%20Mohammedan%20Sporting%20have%20come%20together%20to%20fight%20for%20justice.%20I%20am%20grateful%20to%20everyone.%20This%20fight%20is%20not%20just%20for%20Bengal%2C%20but%20for%20the%20entire%20country.%26quot%3B%20Bose%20continued%3A%20%26quot%3BTogether%2C%20we%20will%20fight%20so%20that%20no%20one%20dares%20to%20commit%20such%20a%20heinous%20act%20again.%20I'm%20a%20footballer%2C%20and%20the%20ground%20means%20everything%20to%20me.%20But%20if%20our%20mothers%20and%20sisters%20don't%20feel%20safe%20in%20our%20state%20or%20country%2C%20there%20is%20nothing%20more%20important%20than%20addressing%20that.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BWe%20all%20have%20to%20come%20together%20and%20fight%20for%20their%20safety.%20We%20must%20protect%20them%20and%20show%20them%20respect.%20I'm%20here%20as%20a%20common%20person%2C%20without%20any%20political%20affiliation.%26quot%3B%20Asked%20about%20his%20feeling%20on%20the%20cancellation%20of%20Durand%20Cup%20derby%20match%20against%20East%20Bengal%20earlier%20scheduled%20to%20be%20played%20on%20Sunday%2C%20he%20said%3A%20%26quot%3BNo%20one%20would%20have%20been%20happier%20than%20me%20if%20the%20match%20had%20taken%20place.%20I%20always%20want%20to%20play%20in%20as%20many%20derbies%20as%20I%20can.%20But%20this%20was%20the%20government's%20decision%2C%20and%20they%20felt%20it%20was%20necessary.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BHowever%2C%20the%20bigger%20cause%20is%20justice%20for%20RG%20Kar%2C%20and%20I%20will%20always%20stand%20for%20that%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20fans%20started%20assembling%20around%204pm%20in%20front%20of%20the%20VIP%20Gate%20of%20the%20Saltlake%20Staidum%20where%20the%20Durand%20Cup%20derby%20match%20bet