colour.%20The%20match%20should%20not%20have%20been%20cancelled.%20If%20the%20fans%20are%20arrested%2C%20it's%20a%20shame%20for%20the%20state's%20law%20and%20order%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20added.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EChaubey%20was%20also%20seen%20standing%20with%20the%20supporters%20and%20pleaded%20in%20front%20of%20the%20police%20van%20not%20to%20arrest%20any%20fan%2C%20who%20were%20later%20seen%20to%20be%20released.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20quarterfinal%20fixtures%20of%20the%20133rd%20Durand%20Cup%20was%20announced%20on%20Sunday%20with%20the%20city%20hosting%20Bengaluru%20FC%20versus%20Kerala%20Blasters%20match%20of%20the%20tournament.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EEast%20Bengal%20will%20play%20their%20quarterfinal%20match%20in%20Shillong%2C%20while%20holders%20Mohun%20Bagan%20will%20play%20Punjab%20FC%20in%20Jamshedpur.%20It%20remains%20to%20be%20seen%20if%20the%20semifinals%20and%20the%20summit%20clash%20scheduled%20on%20August%2031%20at%20the%20Saltlake%20Stadium%20are%20held.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMohun%20Bagan%20and%20East%20Bengal%20are%20in%20the%20opposite%20end%20of%20the%20draw%20and%20could%20head%20for%20a%20potential%20derby%20final.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20postgraduate%20trainee%20doctor%20was%20allegedly%20raped%20and%20murdered%20while%20on%20duty%20at%20the%20RG%20Kar%20MCH%20on%20August%209.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Ci%3E(Except%20for%20the%20headline%2C%20this%20story%20has%20not%20been%20edited%20by%20NDTV%20staff%20and%20is%20published%20from%20a%20syndicated%20feed.)%3C%2Fi%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1724050860000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2024-08%2F9qu9qshg_subhasish-bose_625x300_19_August_24.jpeg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fsports.ndtv.com%2Ffootball%2Fmohun-bagan-captain-subhasish-bose-leads-protest-march-against-kolkata-rape-horror-6365920%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Unprecedented%20scenes%20were%20witnessed%20outside%20the%20Salt%20Lake%20Stadium%20as%20India%20defender%20and%20Mohun%20Bagan%20captain%20Subhasish%20Bose%