20Wissant%2C%20swimming%20a%20whopping%2042%20kilometres.%20(The%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthebetterindia.com%2F88621%2Farati-saha-first-indian-asian-woman-swim-english-channel%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EEnglish%20Channel%3C%2Fa%3E%20is%20actually%2033%20kilometres%20long).%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CIt%20was%20the%20biggest%20mission%20of%20my%20life.%20I%20feel%20fulfilled%20and%20extremely%20happy.%20Everyone%20knows%20me%20today%20as%20Tanvi%E2%80%99s%20father%2C%20what%20else%20do%20I%20need%2C%E2%80%9D%20says%20Kiran.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EWhile%20Tanvi%20was%20too%20tired%20to%20celebrate%20then%2C%20today%2C%20she%20is%20incredibly%20proud%20of%20what%20she%20achieved.%20%E2%80%9CIt%20was%20a%20life-changing%20moment%2C%E2%80%9D%20says%20Tanvi.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ETo%20her%20mother%2C%20it%20felt%20as%20though%20her%20daughter%20had%20been%20born%20again.%20To%20her%20children%2C%20she%20is%20a%20magician%2C%20someone%20for%20whom%20nothing%20is%20impossible.%20For%20everyone%20witnessing%20her%20achievements%2C%20Tanvi%20is%20a%20powerful%20example%20of%20what%20a%20person%20can%20accomplish%20when%20they%20set%20their%20mind%20to%20it.%20So%2C%20what%E2%80%99s%20stopping%20you%3F%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cem%3EEdited%20by%20Pranita%20Bhat%3B%20Images%20Courtesy%20Tanvi%20Deore%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1723816133000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F08%2Ftanvi-deore-1723814698.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthebetterindia.com%2F%3Fp%3D361675%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Nashik-based%20Tanvi%20Deore%20(33)%20rekindled%20her%20passion%20for%20swimming%20after%20an%2018-year%20hiatus%20to%20fulfil%20her%20childhood%20dream%20of%20swimming%20the%20English%20Channel.%20Despite%20facing%20physical%2C%20mental%2C%20and%20logistical%20challenges%2C%20here%E2%80%99s%20how%20she%20successfully%20completed%20the%2