njoy%20peaceful%20evenings%20near%20the%20lake%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20adds.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EKapil%20says%20it%20cost%20the%20organisation%20Rs%204%20crore%20to%20complete%20this%20project.%20%E2%80%9CIt%20is%20an%20expensive%20affair%20that%20can%20only%20be%20achieved%20through%20corporate%20support.%20We%20make%20sure%20to%20involve%20the%20community%20to%20ensure%20the%20sustainability%20of%20the%20rejuvenation%20efforts.%20The%20community%20acts%20as%20additional%20hands%20and%20eyes%20for%20us%2C%20because%20while%20rejuvenation%20is%20easier%2C%20maintaining%20the%20lake%20is%20challenging%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20says.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CWe%20have%20diverted%20some%20of%20the%20incoming%20sewage%20and%20kept%20the%20rest%20to%20ensure%20a%20steady%20flow%20of%20water%20into%20the%20lake.%20To%20achieve%20this%2C%20we%20created%20sedimentation%20ponds%20and%20wetlands%20that%20filter%20the%20incoming%20water%20before%20it%20reaches%20the%20lake.%20Rains%20are%20only%20seasonal%2C%20so%20maintaining%20a%20consistent%20water%20flow%20is%20crucial%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20adds.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-image%5C%22%3E%5Cn%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20sizes%3D%5C%22(max-width%3A%201080px)%20100vw%2C%201080px%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F08%2F1-1_11zon-1723177838.jpg%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%221080%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Kapil%20says%20rejuvenating%20polluted%20lakes%20helps%20with%20groundwater%20recharge%20and%20builds%20resilience%20against%20urban%20flooding.%20%5C%22%20srcset%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F08%2F1-1_11zon-1723177838.jpg%201080w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F08%2F1-1_11zon-1723177838-300x300.jpg%20300w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F08%2F1-1_11zon-1723177838-500x500.jpg%20500w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F08%2F1-1_11zon-1723177838-150x150.jpg%20150w%2